n YouTube. You just have to know the&nbsp;best, most strategic new tactics to do it., MEET YOUR TEACHER, GARYVEE4.09M Followers, BRENDON BURCHARD945K Followers, LEWIS HOMES2.61M Followers, CHALENE JOHNSON763K Followers, JOHN BEVERE616K Followers, PATRICK BET-DAVID3.75M Followers, CHRIS DO2.06M Followers, THIS IS FOR YOU IF..., You Want a Step-by-Step Guide, You Need Inspiration &amp; Motivation, You Want the Best YouTube Strategies, FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS, Join Our Free&nbsp;YouTube Challenge","Join the YouTube 1k Challenge! Free YouTube Class Youtube Book Courses Coaching Contact us Log In This Challenge is now over! Join our free class at ThinkMasterclass.com . IT'S NOT TOO LATE! CLICK HERE TO JOIN THE YOUTUBE 1K CHALLENGE FOR FREE What It Is 5 days of free, live training all about how to ACTUALLY grow and monetize a YouTube channel in 2023. Who It's For You are an entrepreneur, business owner, or someone who&rsquo;s been thinking about starting a YouTube Channel. Happening Now! It's not too late to join. January 23-27 J oin us on Facebook OR a private webpage for 5 days of free live training on starting and growing a YouTube Channel. On-demand replays are available for a limited time. DURING THIS FREE CHALLENGE YOU'LL LEARN How to start and grow a YouTube channel RIGHT and get views and subscribers &nbsp; &nbsp; The best ways to make money with YouTube (even if you don&rsquo;t have a product or business) &nbsp; How to create irresistible videos that get your audience to click and keep them watching &nbsp; And how to do it all in a way that serves your audience, builds a quality personal brand, and helps you live the life you want for yourself and your family CLICK HERE TO JOIN THE FREE CHALLENGE NOW WHAT PAST CHALLENGE TAKERS ARE SAYING WHY YOUTUBE? YouTube is the #1 video website in the world. YouTube has 2 billion logged-in monthly users. This makes it one of the biggest social media platforms. This is why it is more important than ever to include it in your marketing strategy, regardless of your industry or niche. If the massive user count isn&rsquo;t enough to convince you, note that the platform reaches more U.S consumers between the ages of 18 and 49 than all cable TV networks combined. YouTube has launched local versions in more than 100 countries. You can navigate YouTube in a total of 80 different languages. No matter where you are in the world and what language you speak, NOW is the time to build your influence on YouTube. You can make a difference in the world, share your message, and build a sustainable freedom lifestyle - all through the power of YouTube. A recent study revealed that being a content creator is the fastest-growing small business type... and YOU have this crazy opportunity to jump on YouTube for FREE. You can start today on your iPhone and reach countless people all over the globe. This platform has the power to help YOU make a positive impact on the world. We are living through a massive shift in our world. The new wave of YouTube entrepreneurs is rising up and refusing to let the changing state of the world define the future of their families and livelihoods. T here is a window of opportunity to build a YouTube channel that will change your entire future. You don't have to go on this journey alone. And you don't have to start with nothing. We want to introduce you to our tried-and-true formula for growing on YouTube and creating a high-impact channel. The trainings in this challenge have previously only been taught as a part of our $3,997 YouTube Coaching Progra m, but you get access to it FREE for a limited time during this YouTube 1K Challenge. You&rsquo;ll get 5 days of actionable, high-value content, the ability to connect with the Think Media team, and other purpose-driven creators and entrepreneurs. Discover the secrets to getting views, making money, and creating an impact - all through YouTube. CLICK HERE TO JOIN THE YOUTUBE 1K CHALLENGE FOR FREE WHO IS THIS FOR? Real Estate Agents, Coaches &amp; Service Providers In the largest nationwide study of content creators, we found that 42% of participants were MORE likely to work with a service provider if that service provider has a YouTube channel. That's HUGE. As a real estate agent, coach, personal trainer, dietician... you NEED to be on YouTube. Joining this challenge will give you the step-by-step plan of the videos you can create to bring in more leads to your business. Business Owners&nbsp; &amp; Multi-Level Marketers And in a nationwide study of content creators, 75%&nbsp;said that they would be more likely to purchase a product after watching a YouTube video about it. There is massive income-producing opportunity on YouTube for business owners and affiliate marketers alike. Content Creators &amp; Aspiring Creative Entrepreneurs 64% of all participants polled on a national scale said that they watch more YouTube than TV. The eyeballs are on YouTube - you just need to get in front of them. In this Challenge, we teach you how to make the videos that will get noticed, gain subscribers, and ultimately, help you set up a sustainable lifestyle business. Busy Parents, Students &amp; Professionals There is a way to do this. Even if you have just 2 hours a week to give to your channel, you can create a business and a future on YouTube. You just have to know the&nbsp;best, most strategic new tactics to do it. We will have daily giveaways of the best products from top YouTube gear companies. Join the challenge to start receiving&nbsp;daily entries and more opportunities&nbsp;to win! TAKE THE YOUTUBE 1K CHALLENGE & BE ENTERED TO WIN THIS GEAR! MEET YOUR TEACHER &nbsp; &nbsp; Sean Cannell is one of the most watched video content experts in the world and one of his channels was listed by Forbes as one of the ""Top 20 Channels That Will Change Your Business."" He is an international speaker, best-selling author of the book YouTube Secrets and his YouTube channel, Think Media, reaches over 21.5 million people a month. Sean has been hailed as one of the most successful online video experts - first building a multiple six-figure business through affiliate marketing and then going on to build a seven-figure media company focusing on online education that he still runs today. Sean and his team are on a mission to help 10,000 people quit their day jobs to do what they love. He is passionate about giving tactical, practical advice to use video to spread your message. Sean is from Arlington Washington and currently lives in Las Vegas, NV with his wife Sonja, their sons Sean Bradley and John Stephen, and their dog, Sophie. GARYVEE 4.09M Followers ""GET THE 'YOUTUBE SECRETS' BOOK. I'M SERIOUS!"" BRENDON BURCHARD 945K Followers ""SEAN'S THE YOUTUBE GUY!"" LEWIS HOMES 2.61M Followers ""SEAN'S THE MAN WHEN IT COMES TO YOUTUBE"" CHALENE JOHNSON 763K Followers JOHN BEVERE 616K Followers PATRICK BET-DAVID 3.75M Followers CHRIS DO 2.06M Followers THIS IS FOR YOU IF... You Want a Step-by-Step Guide You Need Inspiration &amp; Motivation You Want the Best YouTube Strategies FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS Who is this for? This is for anyone wanting to start or grow a YouTube channel! &nbsp;We want to help purpose-driven entrepreneurs make an impact on the world by sharing their story on YouTube. Whether you haven't started yet, you're a complete beginner, or you're an advanced YouTuber, this challenge is right for you. Who is this NOT for? This is NOT a get-rich-quick scheme, a magic key that will allow you to grow without doing any work, or a sure-fire way to be ""famous."" If your only goal is to be a famous YouTuber without really working for it, this might not be right for you... How do I join the challenge? Click any of the blue buttons on this page and enter your info so we can send you all the details on the challenge! How do I enter the YouTube Studio giveaway? Just click any of the blue challenge buttons on this page and you'll be taken to a sign-up form. Once you enter your name and best email, you'll be entered to win! You can also check out www.WinThisTech.com &nbsp;for additional info. But we also have DAILY giveaways that will happen on each challenge session - so even more opportunities to win! You must show up live to the training session to be eligible. How do I watch the challenge sessions? Just click any of the blue buttons on this page and you'll be taken to a sign-up form. Once you enter your name and best email, you'll receive further instructions in your email on how to join our challenge Facebook group. The Facebook group is where all of the challenge sessions are going to be taking place along with more ways to enter giveaways, so you'll definitely want to join the group! Not on Facebook? We are offering a watch-only, limited YouTube 1K Challenge experience on a private watch page. Sign up to receive more information on how you can get access to the sessions without having to have a Facebook account. Why do you need my email? There will be a lot going on for this challenge (Facebook group, daily training, giveaways, etc). We need a way to get you all the information you may need, so email is required. We also&nbsp;may text you (if you provided your number) when we are live in the Facebook group so you don't miss a thing! What if I can’t attend every day? That's okay! Just come for as much of the challenge content as you're able to. And if you miss any of the live sessions, replays of each training will be&nbsp; available for a limited time. We will even offer a few additional days over the weekend once the challenge ends for you to catch up and binge watch our trainings! You'll see more details&nbsp;on this after you sign up for the challenge. CLICK HERE TO JOIN THE FREE CHALLENGE & BE A PART OF THIS MOVEMENT &copy; 2025 Clearvision Media, Inc Terms Privacy Earnings Disclaimer Join Our Free&nbsp;YouTube Challenge Plus, get instant bonus resources when you sign up today! (The sooner you sign up, the more entries you get for our YouTube Studio Giveaway) By submitting this form you&#39;re agreeing to receive emails and text messages from Think Media. Join the Challenge Today"
