on to become a paying client. Enter Your Details To Register CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Presentation Profits Is For You If... You want to drive sales into a new or existing business. ​​​ You want to be seen as a trusted authority. ​ You want people reaching out to you rather than cold messaging them. ​ You want to get paid for sharing your coaching, consulting or expert advice. ​You want to automate the process of getting clients. ​You dream of making 10x the income of Mr and Mrs Average. ​You believe you can truly help people or businesses with your advice. You don’t know exactly what to sell yet but you know you have a lot to offer. CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Proof That Using A Serve &amp; Sell Presentation Wins New Clients...! Steven Green: Starting Point: Left the army and wanted to become a motivational coach. What we did together: Created an inspirational content-rich presentation. Where is he now: Made over 7 million in sales from a standing start. Sammy Blindell: Starting Point: Burnt out full service marketing agency owner. What we did together: Extracted from her head her genius and turned it into a course instead. Where is she now: Made over 13 million in sales from a single presentation selling her courses. Simon Coulson: Starting Point: Owned an internet marketing training company. What we did together: Built one single serve &amp; sell presentation that doubled his conversion. Where is he now: Made millions and now teaches people how to write songs. Nick James: Starting Point: Failing part-time coaching business that was losing money. What we did together: Taught him how to sell coaching and training with a presentation. Where is he now: Owns a thriving 8-figure training and coaching company. CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Jessen James: Starting Point: Owned a successful hair salon but was bored and wanted a new challenge. What we did together : Transitioned into a business advisor selling training courses. Where is he now: Makes 2 million a year doing what he loves. Fiona Challis: Starting Point: Working 1-2-1 as a coach to blue-chip corporates . What we did together: Built a training out of her knowledge and designed a presentation to sell it. Where is she now: Made over a million and now has a 2nd course on finding love..! Paul Preston: Starting Point: Working as a cleaner, making £6 per hour &amp; part time property investor. What we did together: Built a training course on property investment and a presentation to sell it. Where is he now: Made over 8-figures, so has now become an actor in movies..! Michelle Watson: Starting Point: London Underground train driver, part time life coach and author. What we did together: Built a full-time business as a book writing trainer/coach Where is she now: Makes over 6-figures a year, owns property in Jamaica..! CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Daniel Konieczny: Starting Point: Working for Unite the Union making €45,000 a year. What we did together: Taught him to my Serve and Sell System so how could speak on stage at other people's events. Where is he now: He is now a full-time motivational speaker and has made over €10 million. Dawn McGruer: Starting Point: Social media manager but her presentations not converting into clients. What we did together: Created the Dynamic Digital Marketing Mandates framework with a presentation that sells it. Where is she now: Award winning 7-figure marketing expert. Georgia Kirke: Starting Point: Fledgling book writing coach just starting out. What we did together: Built a webinar to sell a £2,000 and £20,000 service. Where is she now: An award winning, multi-million pound book coach. Sally Lawson: Starting Point: Letting agency owner. What we did together: Built a training program for letting agents to grow their business. Where is she now: Sells a program worth £27,000 and has made £12 million total. CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Here’s What You'll Be Learning At Presentation Profits Please note as this a live training - timings may vary slightly. CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Why is it FREE? For complete transparency, Presentation Profits is FREE to attend because once I’ve taught you how to construct a Serve &amp; Sell presentation for your business, you may still want to hire me or a member of my team to give you feedback on the design and delivery of it. If there is a good fit we would be delighted to work with you more closely. However you do not need to buy any of our courses or mentoring options. In fact, we encourage you to attend this virtual presentation, make copious notes and implement what we show you because it will rapidly accelerate the growth of your new or existing business. CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML About Your Presenter: Andy Harrington is a Sunday Times best selling author. He has spoken in giant arenas around the world including The London o2 Arena. He has worked with Richard Branson, Tony Robbins, Nadia Swarovski, Hollywood movie stars and two presidents of the United States (even though he lives in the United Kingdom). He is the founder of The Professional Speakers Academy and has launched or accelerated the coaching, consulting, and expert advisory services of thousands of people worldwide. He has been featured in The Times, Forbes Magazine, GQ Magazine and a documentary on the BBC1. Andy Harrington Performing At The o2 Arena CUSTOM JAVASCRIPT / HTML Copyright 2020 | All Rights Reserved Jet Set Speaker Ltd Need help? Email: support@andyharrington.com Terms Of Use | Privacy Policy | Disclaimer This site is not a part of the Facebook™ website or Facebook™ Inc. Additionally, this site is NOT endorsed by Facebook™ in any way. FACEBOOK™ is a trademark of FACEBOOK™, Inc. Copyright 2020 | All Rights Reserved Jet Set Speaker Ltd Terms Of Use | Privacy Policy | Disclaimer Need help? Email: support@andyharrington.com | This site is not a part of the Facebook™ website or Facebook™ Inc. Additionally, this site is NOT endorsed by Facebook™ in any way. FACEBOOK™ is a trademark of FACEBOOK™, Inc. Working..."
