g Model Upside Down This Is Something Completely New, Completely Different, Completely Unlike Anything You've Ever Heard of Before - Read The Story Below To Discover The NEPQ Black Book Of Questions This Is Something Completely New, Completely Different, Completely Unlike Anything You've Ever Heard of Before - Read The Story Below To Discover The NEPQ Black Book Of Questions Dear Future Black Book Owner From: The laptop of Jeremy Miner Re: Doubling Your Current Commissions Without Selling Your Soul In The Process ( and why this is your only way out ) Would it surprise you to learn, that I hit my first 7 figure year as a W2 sales rep using the information revealed in this 57 page black book? Skeptical? You should be. After all, you can’t believe everything you read on the internet :-) But can we be real with each other for a moment because there's a real threat to salespeople the world over... And that threat is being average. You see, the average sales rep makes less than 42k/year. And I don't know about you... But I didn't get into this game to be average. And I definitely didn't get into this game to earn less than a McDonald's store manager. So Let Me Prove To You It's Possible To Blow Past The Competition Using This New Selling Model But first, read this disclaimer: I have the benefit of over 12 years in the trenches using the sales model you're about to get your hands on today. The average person who buys any “how to” information gets little to no results. I’m using these references for example purposes only. Your results will vary and depend on many factors …including but not limited to your background, experience, and work ethic. All purchases entails risk as well as massive and consistent effort and action. If you're not willing to accept that, please DO NOT GET THIS BLACK BOOK. And yes, it took me time and energy to achieve my results. But you're in sales... so I know you're not scared of a little work, in fact... I'll be you're looking forward to it. With that said... How I Did It By Using A New And Completely Counterintuitive Selling Model That I’m About To Share With You On This Very Page… The same NEPQ selling model that sales professionals from all over the world are now using to ditch the pitch and sell more while talking less… ...And in turn scale up their take home commissions faster than ever before... ...All while asking simple questions that put them in control of every single sales call so they can focus on finally living the life you were promised as a sales professional... ...And best of all have everyone else asking you what the heck you're doing differently since last month to climb to the top of the scoreboard. You'll literally have ZERO competition once you start selling this way... Just Like Johnny, Who Downloaded The NEPQ Black Book, Put It To Work And Soon After Hit His First 6 Figure Month In Commissions And Then Posted This In Our Private FB Group: And even though he's raking in what some reps do in 2-3 years in a month, that's not the best part... The best part is he's breezing past gatekeepers, and is in full control every conversation he enters thanks to using NEPQ. That's right, just by changing his sales approach and using a simple question-based framework... he's transformed his entire life without pushy outdated methods. And Johnny isn’t the only one either… This Is Jordan Tanner, Another NEPQ Member, Who Downloaded The Black Book of Questions Book Not Too Long Ago… ...And soon more than doubled his commissions and bought himself a new house... all from learning to ask the right questions ... Here’s a post he posted in our private FB Community (which you will have access to once you download the black book)... Here’s another NEPQ Black Book owner who started using these strategies… Meet Anna Who Went From 2k per month to hitting her first 36k commission month Even Just using NEPQ questions 30% of the time Johnny, Jordan, and Anna are a group of over 2,000 new wave of NEPQ Black Book owners who are Selling differently In Over 115 Industries… And you can BET... This NEPQ selling model is unlike any method you've heard of before… …This is something completely different, because… We don’t focus on pushing our way through a sale ​ We don’t worry about objections anymore (this method eliminates them before they come up) ​ We don’t stumble through the close ​ We don’t waste endless hours chasing and burning through leads ​ And we definitely don’t chant ""Always Be Closing!"" In fact: we never even pull the outdated tactics out of the toolbox ever again after using this method. Instead We Ask Simple Questions That Melt Sales Resistance And Have The Prospect Handle Their Own Objections To Pull Themselves Over the line ... Like I said… This is something completely different and it has the power to change the trajectory of your sales career forever… …and I know that’s true… Because it changed everything for me. The NEPQ model allowed me to get rid of 99% of all the BS that I hated when it comes to selling in today's economy… Trying to persuade prospects with flashy features and benefits ​​Talking so much on calls that my throat was bone dry at the end of the day ​​Feeling like a glorified product pusher ​​Forcing myself to apply pressure on calls that kept me awake at night ​​Doing presentations and pitching, almost like I was paid to perform instead of sell The NEPQ Method Freed Me From All That and It Allowed Me To Unlock A New Level Of Commissions I didn't Even Realize Was Possible... Without Resorting To Pushy, Sleazy Tactics I hated Here’s what my life used to look like (and If you’ve been a rep or taken calls for more than a week, then I’m sure you can relate)… I call this the “Go Painfully Pushy Method”: Step 1 - Start with a predictable ""line"" or opening ""tactic"" Step 2 - Immediately hit with sales resistance because Step 3 - Fight to keep them on the line and speak with you Step 4 - Push forward (if you don't get hung up on...) Step 5 - Reach for the script and start pitching features Step 6 - Prospect loses interest... so you throw in benefits Step 7 - You might make it to the close if you're lucky and then... objection overload ! Step 8 - Pull out every last trick in the book and lose the sale... or close and feel drained having fought and pushed your way through the entire sales process. The ""Painfully Pushy Method"" not only sucked , but kept me stuck for 3 years - forcing me to feel completely out of control of my calls and earning potential... making only $3k per month while working my ass off. To be honest… ...I almost gave up on this whole idea of earning high 6 or even 7 figures as a sales rep ... But before I gave up.. I wanted to try something. Something that - if it worked. It would change everything. And as you're about to find out, what I tried... ... It worked... And I spent 12 years turning it into a system... The same system that you'll be able to take right onto your calls tomorrow if you choose... And I Put This Entire System In A 57 Page Black book Called The NEPQ Black Book Of Questions And You Can Dive Into It In Just A Few Moments From Now… But before you do. I’d like to introduce myself and tell you about how all this came to be. My name’s Jeremy Miner… You probably haven’t heard that name before. That’s by design. My life’s pretty good (now)… I bought my dream house that backs onto the 16th hole of a pristine golf course... I do have decent cars (but I prefer to put my surplus commissions into investments)... ...and I now spend half the year at my lake house with my girls. And I don't say that to brag, I just want you to understand what's possible with the right sales skills. Here's a few pictures to take a peak into my life thanks to NEPQ... And As We Get To Know Each Other… You’ll Quickly Realize That I’m The Luckiest Person On Earth - So Let’s Talk About Where I Was At The Start Of My Sales Career... I was barely 22 years old and living in Orem, Utah selling alarms in college. I had no clue what I was doing, and thought that pushing my way through the sales conversation. I had no coaches or mentors I could count on, and unfortunately dug into the outdated books on sales that are still using 100 year old methods that just didn't work for me. I had no control over what I was earning and to be honest... that was the most frustrating part. ... and I kept banging my head against the wall because all my managers were telling me that ""this was the way"" or ""these are the greats""... But it meant I couldn’t pursue what I knew in my gut was a different approach and made me realize... There’s a stupid myth out there.. that you need to ""Always Be Closing""... And if you want to really make it in sales... Always Be Closing and pushing your way through an outdated process is never the answer... I know, because I tried. I gave it everything I had. I gave it my BEST shot. And it didn’t work. Because I played by the rules and I did everything right... I ended up Frustrated And Burned Out With Nothing To Show For All My Hard Work And I Hated It… I hated it because I was doing exactly what I was taught... I had goals, dreams and aspirations...I wanted more out of life... ...and one day I realized that following conventional sales wisdom in the new economy just wasn't going to work. So I did what everyone else out there does in this situation. I started looking for a way out. I looked everywhere and a few months later I had an A-HA moment I'll never forget. My sales manager picked me up and popped in a Tony Robbins CD (yes, I'm dating myself a bit here)... And I might butcher this a bit but Tony said something like this... ""Most people fail, because they don't learn the RIGHT skills necessary to succeed."" And that's when it hit me... Maybe, just MAYBE ... What I was being taught by my company and the sales gurus were just not working anymore. The information was outdated... ...irrelevant... And soul-sucking to use in real calls. That's when I dusted off my College Degree in Human Behaviour and Psychology, and got to work on testing out what would become my new sales approach in the real world... With real dollars on the line. After LOTS Of Trial And Error... I Discovered Specific Questions That Melted Sales Resistance And Closed Deals In Half The Time Just think about it: Does the consumer buy the same way that they used to? No, consumers are more informed than ever before in history. Do we have the same buying behaviors as we did in the 1950's? I would argue not... so why are we still using the methods taught then? Do prospects rely on us to educate them? How could that be true anymore, when everything is a quick Google search away? Is competition the same that it was just 20 years ago? Let's be real... there's more competition than ever with thousands of new businesses entering the market every day. That's why this question-based approach to sales in a way prospects never heard before was the perfect thing for me... Now, if you're struggling to make it in sales let me be the first to tell you... It's NOT Your Fault You're being taught 100+ year old sales techniques when consumer buying behavior has evolved...! Isn't it time we evolved our sales approach? that was the birth of The NEPQ Approach To Sales And The Black Book Of Questions Once I realized I could actually close deals like this, I just couldn't help myself. I was relentlessly testing question after question in the trenches... Don't get me wrong... I lost a lot of sales in the process by asking the wrong questions at the wrong time... I had no idea how to figure it out on paper and I knew that the only way to really make this work was to pursue on no matter what... All I knew was how to ask questions and I aggressively took note after note on how each question I asked at specific times affected my closing rates. And even though I had the right idea... I still had to put in the work and stay true to my mission. Looking back, those first 12 months were bru