 love about the Mind Shifting system is, that you have a very efficent process to solve different kinds of problems or traumas with the different Mind Shifting methods. The main reason why I got interested in Mind Shifting was, that you can use the methode also on yourself. The training course is great, as you learn and practice all the tools you need to help clients to solve their problems. I can 1000 % recommend the Mind Shifting course for everybody who is working in the coaching business."" -- Josef Voglsam, Entrepreneur “Not only can I help others with the methods but I can also help myself.” “One of the things I loved about the training and the Mind Shifting system is that, not only can I help others with the methods but I can also help myself. I can use the methods to work on some of my own short comings, mindset, perspective, problems, goals and so on. One of the best things about the course also is that, the methods are being demonstrated by Stevie during the training sessions and we get to practice the methods with other coaches during class. Stevie would guide us during practice to make we understand the methods and use them the correct way. ” -- Rani Jamal, Mind Shifting Coach I&#x27;m Ready to 10x My Clients&#x27; Results How will the Mind Shifting method help me? 1 You're an experienced life coach, therapist or healer As an experienced coach, therapist or healer... The Mind Shifting method will give you a powerful new tool for facilitating rapid transformation for your clients. Leading to more referrals and more booked sessions... And a transition into group coaching if you desire. 2 You want to become a coach, therapist or healer If you've not yet started coaching full time yet, or haven't completed your initial training then you're in luck! Because learning this Mind Shifting method will give you an unfair advantage over coaches and therapist that have been working full-time for 20 years! And at a fraction of the cost of life coaching and talk-therapy training, that only leaves you struggling to get clients without a unique offering! 3 You facilitate group coaching, workshops or retreats Mind Shifting will give you a powerful tool to use in group sessions. Which you can build an entire group coaching programme, workshop or retreat around. Ensuring you get transformational breakthroughs for everyone. All at the same time! I&#x27;m Ready to 10x My Clients&#x27; Results Frequently asked questions How can Mind Shifting Training help me as a coach, therapist, or healer? Mind Shifting Training equips you with a transformative technique that can dissolve your clients' problems and blockages in just 5-10 minutes. This method is faster and more effective than mainstream methods. By incorporating Mind Shifting into your practice, you'll be helping your clients achieve rapid, tangible transformations. How is Mind Shifting different from other methods like affirmations, NLP, hypnosis, or life coaching? While life coaching, talk-therapy, NLP, hypnosis, and other mainstream methods can serve as useful tools, they often take a long time to produce changes and don't permanently clear the subconscious blockage that cause people's problems. Mind Shifting, on the other hand, directly targets these subconscious blockages tha keep your clients stuck, enabling deep transformation in much less time. What specific problems or blockages can I help my clients to overcome with Mind Shifting? Mind Shifting is versatile and can address a variety of issues, including anxiety, stress, relationship conflicts, emotional triggers, heartbreak, negative thinking, low self-esteem, lack of motivation and much more besides. Essentially, any problem a client is experiencing can be tackled effectively with this method (apart from addictions which require specialist training). How much time will it take me to learn the Mind Shifting method? This Mind Shifting training is designed with your busy schedule in mind. By downloading the Mind Shifting method and watching the bite-sized video lessons you can be using Mind Shifting to clear real problems in less than one hour. And you can consume the rest of the training videos at your own pace. How will this course impact my practice financially? By incorporating Mind Shifting into your practice, you'll be able to offer a unique, effective, and rapid transformational method to your clients. If marketed well this will attract more clients, increase client retention and referrals, and even allow you to charge higher fees due to the added value you're providing. Can I use Mind Shifting for group coaching? Yes! Mind Shifting works just the same way when applied to groups. Which means you can clear a whole group of people's problems all at the same time, even though everyone's problem is different! Because of this you can also use Mind Shifting to run group workshops and retreats. Can I use Mind Shifting on myself? Yes! Mind Shifting works just the same when you apply it to yourself. Which means you never have to stay stuck with the same problems or blockages for long. You can just apply the Mind Shifting method to them to keep moving forward. Without having to pay for coaching or therapy! What if the Mind Shifting method doesn&#x27;t work for me? Mind Shifting works for everyone. But your investment in Mind Shifting is completely risk-free. If you're not satisfied, you can make use of the 14-day money back guarantee and get a full refund. As long as you have actually tried using the method! This ensures that you have enough time to try out the method and gauge its effectiveness without any financial risk. After this initial training is there more to learn afterwards if I want? Yes, consider this training your Mind Shifting 'boot camp' or 'basic training'. It will teach you the core Mind Shifting method, which you can use to clear people's problems in 5-10 minutes. If after that you want to learn all Mind Shifting has to offer there are 5 more Mind Shifting methods you can learn, with specialist applications like healing trauma, transforming limiting beliefs, shifting identities, achieving goals, and clearing whole groups of related problems at the same time. This advanced training is for people who want to become certified as a Mind Shifting coach and consists of weekly live training calls over Zoom for a period of 8-weeks. If you want to do the full training course and become a certified Mind Shifting coach, then doing this initial training to learn the core Mind Shifting method is the first step! I&#x27;m Ready to 10x My Clients&#x27; Results Still Have Doubts? That's Understandable... Here Are The Facts: This all sounds too good to be true. ""Rapid transformation in 10 minutes?"" I get it. It's natural to be skeptical. But Mind Shifting is backed by over a decade of extensive testing and results. This isn't some flash in the pan fad. The techniques have been proven through thousands of hours of development and application. The step-by-step training teaches you through how to use the Mind Shifting method in less than an hour. And we are available for support if you ever get stuck. You're never just left on your own. You owe it to the clients counting on you to be open to new, innovative approaches. Even if it goes against conventional assumptions about how transformation works. Breakthroughs happen when you're willing to shake up outdated paradigms and try new methods. Here's the bottom line: Mind Shifting is disrupting the coaching and therapy industry because of how powerfully and quickly it works. The techniques have been validated again and again. And the no risk, 100% money-back guarantee makes trying it a no-brainer. If you feel even the slightest desire to say yes, go with that instinct. It could change everything. For just one hour of your time, you have so much to gain. I&#x27;m Ready to 10x My Clients&#x27; Results This Is Your Moment The time for offering the same generic life coaching services as everybody else is over. Equip yourself today with the fastest transformational method on the planet. Experience the joy of facilitating lasting breakthroughs and fulfill your purpose at a whole new level. Then watch your business grow when your clients are amazed at their results and tell all their friends about you! I&#x27;m Ready to 10x My Clients&#x27; Results Get Instant Access to the Mind Shifting Method For Clearing Problems And All Bonuses Now! Mind Shifting method for clearing problems ($1,250 Value) Bonus #1: Mind Shifting Video Training on Problem Shifting ($850 Value) Bonus #2: Lifetime access to the online practice community ($850 Value) Bonus #3: Video training on how to use Mind Shifting on yourself ($650 Value) Bonus #4: Optional Live Workshops to practice Mind Shifting ($750 Value) Bonus #5: Optional help from a Mind Shifting Success Coach ($600 Value) Total value: $4,950 Usual price: $200 Special Offer - Get 50% Off Today One payment of $97! COMPLETE YOUR ORDER NOW! Get the Mind Shifting method and all bonuses now! © 2024 MIND SHIFTING LLC. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED. Terms of Use Privacy Policy Cookie Policy Disclaimer START MIND SHIFTING NOW! Special Offer - Get 50% Off Today - $200 $97! 1 INFORMATION Your login details 2 Checkout Get Instant Access Now Next"
