der &amp; CEO | Launch &amp; Scale™ Verified As an entrepreneur, I constantly feel overwhelmed and second guess if what I’m working on will move me toward my goals, with Commit Action’s focus, now I don’t feel that way as I’m working Coaching Without Accountability Doesn’t Work Have you tried coaching and programs that get you hyped with big “aha” moments... only to realize weeks later that nothing has actually changed? That’s because most coaches (and “masterminds”) offer zero real accountability, so it’s easy to self-sabotage and stay stuck at the same level for years. Our evidence-based coaching system gives you the structure and accountability you need to get clarity, execute fast and finally achieve what you know you’re truly capable of. See Plans &amp; Pricing Accountability For Your Business Goals 01 The Ultimate Science-Backed Productivity Ritual The first ingredient of incredible productivity is our method. Our weekly planning ritual was developed with researchers at Harvard &amp; NYU, and field-tested by thousands of entrepreneurs. It’s designed to help you zoom out, turn chaos into clarity, and stack the odds in your favour so you can finish 100% of your most important work every single week. Here’s the core of our weekly planning ritual: 1 Analyze Use our systematic audit process to identify what’s driving results and what’s creating friction. This smart question framework surfaces patterns in your work habits and reveals hidden obstacles to progress. 2 Clarify Apply our filtering framework to cut through the noise and identify your highest impact opportunities. This prioritization method aligns daily actions with bigger objectives, ensuring your efforts compound toward meaningful outcomes. 3 Commit Plan out your top priorities in a way that transforms decisions into executable plans. This structuring process creates time-bounded commitments with clear deliverables and accountability for effortless motivation. 02 Your Personal Trainer For Business Growth