ty to hit your goals easier and faster. For ambitious solopreneurs, freelancers, executives and creatives. Learn More Business Coaching $575 / month Includes 30 Day Zero Risk Guarantee High ROI strategy coaching for entrepreneurs who want to delegate smarter and scale faster. Get the clarity &amp; focus you need to execute, iterate &amp; hit your biggest growth goals. Learn More Elite Coaching Starting at $2,300 / month Includes 30 Day Zero Risk Guarantee Bespoke coach support for elite entrepreneurs with multi-business portfolios. Get custom programs to solve high-level challenges. Embed your coach into your systems and across your team. Learn More Discover Scientific Productivity Understand our system in just a few hours. Get the exact frameworks, templates, and step-by-step processes our coaches use to help entrepreneurs hit their most ambitious goals. Watch Our Free Course A New Approach To Productivity Most productivity solutions add complexity instead of clarity. They demand more willpower, more systems to manage, and more mental effort, so they fail as soon as the initial excitement wears off. Our approach is different: Human-Powered: You get a real person who understands your business and acts as a second brain, so it’s quick, easy, and done-with-you. No Will Power Required: Our coaching is designed to make productivity easier, not harder. Your coach does all the heavy lifting, you just have to show up. Research-Backed: Developed with Harvard and NYU using proven principles of goal achievement, not fleeting productivity trends. Minimum Effective Dose: A weekly ritual designed for consistency, not perfection. Smart and sustainable wins that compound exponentially over time. Results-Focused: We measure success by outcomes, not activity. Your coach helps you execute the work that truly moves your business forward. Commit Action Coaching vs Traditional Business Coaching Most entrepreneurs mistake traditional guru-based advice for REAL coaching — and that misunderstanding costs them thousands. Features Traditional Business Coaching: Commit Action Coaching: Prices ✗ Charges premium rates ($1,000-5,000/month) for (overwhelming) advice-based guidance ✓ Focuses exclusively on clarity &amp; execution at a fraction of the cost (starts at $199/month) Method ✗ Focuses on teaching strategies that worked for them years ago ✓ Uses research-backed productivity methods that accelerate success in any business model Strategy ✗ Provides strategy but almost zero accountability ✓ Helps you develop and implement YOUR strategies effectively The difference? Commit Action’s business and accountability coaches help individuals stay on track with their goals and commitments. They provide structure, guidance, and feedback, ensuring that the individual remains focused and makes consistent progress. See Plans &amp; Pricing Meet Our Expert Coaches All our coaches are full-time, highly-trained and dedicated career professionals.Joining Commit Action means getting an expert productivity coach on your team. What makes our coaches different: Rigorously selected - We hire just 1 coach for every 200 applicants Extensively trained - 3-month intensive program in our evidence-based methodology Continuously developed - Each coach has their own mentor and daily team reviews to optimize your results Founded by Peter Shallard (&quot; The Shrink for Entrepreneurs &quot;), our methodology was developed with guidance from experts in clinical psychology, neuroscience, and positive psychology. Our team has helped over 10,000 entrepreneurs and executives achieve everything from their first 6-figure breakthrough to successful exits and major life transformations. The Leadership Team Who screen, hire, train &amp; continuously mentor our coaches: Your First 30 Days Are Guaranteed This type of coaching is unique, and if it works as well for you as it has for so many of our clients, you&#x27;ll be blown away by the results. So we&#x27;ve made it a no-brainer for anyone to try! All our coaching services come with a 30-day risk-free guarantee so you can see for yourself: 1 Experience the difference a dedicated accountability partner makes 2 Feel what it&#x27;s like to consistently execute your most important work 3 Notice how quickly clarity and momentum replace overthinking and procrastination See Plans &amp; Pricing Risk-Free Guarantee: We&#x27;re so confident in our approach that we offer a complete satisfaction guarantee. Try Commit Action for 30 days with our 1-to-1 coaching plans and if you don&#x27;t feel totally satisfied with your results, just cancel and email us within the first 30 days. We’ll promptly refund your payment in full. Trusted by 1,000s of Ambitious Professionals Excellent | 262 reviews on Trustpilot Yoav Koni Real Estate Developer Verified Working with Summer at Commit Action has completely changed my life. She has shown the perfect balance between keeping me focused and being flexible enough to help me become the person I want to be and achieve my biggest... Mark Jayne CEO | Jayne Capital Verified Commit Action has helped me gain clarity and productivity from day one and is definitely the highest ROI investment I’ve ever made. As a solo entrepreneur it’s very hard to keep everything together and they help me tremendously. Stephane L. President | WebTarget Inc. Verified I consider Commit Action to be my secret weapon enabling me to leap ahead on my purposeful and driven journey as an entrepreneur (for over 20 years now). The ROI for the Commit Action service is over 10x in my opinion. Read More Success Stories FAQ What exactly is accountability coaching and how does it work? An accountability coach is like a personal trainer for productivity: Someone who works with you every week to create the clarity, structure and focus. They help you execute consistently on your biggest goals. The best business coaches also provide a ton of accountability. Without proper accountability, business coaching is just sharing strategy ideas with zero follow through. Commit Action invented accountability coaching in 2014. Our methodology is evidence-based and was developed in collaboration with cognitive science researchers at Harvard Medical School and NYU (Positive Psychology). What does an accountability coach do? An accountability coach helps you stay on track with your goals and commitments. It’s like hiring someone whose sole job is optimizing your focus, clarifying your priorities and structuring your schedule. They help you move forward on the boldest, best ideas you have… that otherwise tend to get self sabotaged. The coach typically sets up regular check-ins to review accomplishments, address challenges, and set the path forward. Particularly for entrepreneurs, success isn’t just about being merely “productive”. It’s about working on the RIGHT things. A great accountability coaching helps prioritize the best, most effective use of your time. How much does accountability coaching cost? The cost of an accountability coach can vary widely based on factors such as the coach&#x27;s experience, the complexity of the client&#x27;s goals, and the frequency of coaching sessions. Fees can range from $50 to $500 per session or more. Some coaches might offer packages that bundle several sessions at a discounted rate. When considering the fee, it&#x27;s crucial to assess the value and outcomes you expect from the coaching relationship along with the skills/experience of the coach. At Commit Action, our plans start at $199 per month and you get 1-to-1 coaching sessions on the phone every week. Not only that, your accountability coaches are available via text or email throughout the week. We also offer strategic business coaching plans for entrepreneurs, with longer sessions and coaches with more business expertise. How long are the coaching calls? The weekly calls are designed to be quick; a &quot;minimum effective dose&quot; of structure and planning. This follows the behavioral science principle that you maximize long term results by making the behavior that drives them easy. New customers would surely love to spend two hours really diving into our system, planning out their week to a level of outrageous precision. But how many weeks could they feasibly keep that up? By optimizing for consistency with a tightly focused 20-minute ritual, we&#x27;ve created a proven methodology for incrementally increasing your personal effectiveness… with results that compound over time. Commit Action customers who keep the ritual going for a year become unrecognizable to their former selves: they transform into execution powerhouses. Our Business Coaching plans offer 50% longer calls (30 minutes) to get more strategic. Our Elite plans can go anywhere from 60 mins a week and up. The focused 20-minute ritual is best for most people. Are there any long-term commitments or contracts? No. Commit Action is month-to-month (or year-to-year if you choose to pay annually and benefit from a 20% discount). There are no setup fees, cancellation fees, or long term contracts. You can quit at any time. We also offer a 30-day money back guarantee on all our coaching plans, so you are safe to try the service out risk free. There is absolutely nothing to lose and everything to gain. Do I need to already have a business to work with you? No, we have a lot of people who are just starting businesses, as well as clients who are creatives and executives doing other stuff. You can use Commit Action to help you excel in any area or endeavor that you want. As a premium service, we generally like to work with clients where there is a clear return-on-investment for the fee they pay us for our support. If you have ambition, autonomy, and a path to long term reward then we can help you make your big plans happen. Can I speak with someone before I sign up? Here’s a quick note from Commit Action’s CEO, Peter Shallard: One entrepreneur to another: talking to tire-kicking leads is a bit of an operational nightmare. We’d rather our coaches talk exclusively to customers, and we just show you how good the coaching is first hand. Otherwise, it’d mean hiring a sales team, paying them out of our coaching fees and charging our customers more. That’s why we do a no questions asked 30 day guarantee, and built a solid and smooth onboarding process where you get a 60 min call with your coach to start. It’s literally zero risk to just sign up and get a first hand experience of deep diving into the coaching. Your coach will answer all your questions, and some you didn’t ask! We’re very confident in the skills of our coaches but if it’s not a fit, just cancel your membership (in a few clicks) and request a full refund. If you have a quick question, you can always get in touch via our Contact Page. Commit Action About Us See The Science Success Stories Entrepreneur Personality Test Frequently Asked Questions Products Accountability Coaching Business Coaching Elite Coaching Scientific Productivity Course Head Start 2026 Training Accountability Articles &amp; Resources How To Hire An Accountability Coach ADHD Business Coaching Time Management Coaching Accountability Partners Vs. Accountability Coaches Local Dallas Accountability Coaching Los Angeles Accountability Coaching Toronto Accountability Coaching Atlanta Accountability Coaching NYC Accountability Coaching Miami Accountability Coaching Alternatives Young Presidents Organization Alternative Vistage Alternative Entrepreneurs Organization Alternative Tony Robbins Coaching Alternative Commit Action © 2025 - All Rights Reserved. Contact 30 Day Guarantee Privacy Policy Terms and Conditions"
