d rising gas prices. But that's it! Then for 30 days you can build funnel after funnel absolutely free. Then it's just a small $297 /mo to keep doing your thang. But as you know, we don't leave you hanging... Throughout the 30 days we'll be with you, side-by-side, holding your hand every step of the way so you can build and launch your first funnel with confidence. Every question and concern you may have, we'll be there for you... Any ""tech"" issue... we'll be there for you. And any issues regarding ""what to say,"" ""how to say it,"" or ""what page comes next?""... we'll be there for you. This is the Your First Funnel program, where we will take you from an online newbie to a veteran funnel building monster in 30 days or my name isn't Russell T. Brunson III (it's just Russell Brunson, but I like all of the name flare hahaha...) What if I'm not ""techie"" and perhaps a bit slow? That's normal! Most of our first-timers are a little ""shy"" or embarrassed, but the truth is— we all have to start somewhere. You'd be surprised how many ""newbies"" end up becoming ClickFunnels pros in a matter of days! There's no shame if you're new or have never worked with online business software before. We'll answer EVERYTHING for you, including tech questions, funnel-building questions, and how to approach your market the right way. All of our coaches are incredibly patient and love the feeling they get when they help someone brand new. Not to mention, you'll be among good company because most people that come through Your First Funnel are new, too! We never make anyone feel silly or dumb about where they are. Every step is exciting and new and we're so pumped to be working alongside you every step of the way. That's why we do what we do! Can you hold my hand every step of the way? Yes! Well, my team and I can do it digitally. I'm only one person and I hate flying. BUT! Our program is designed to feel as though I'm right there with you every step of your funnel-building journey. Imagine me sitting right next to you and saying things like, ""oooh that's a great headline! I love it."" Or... ""Hmmmm... how about we add an opt-in button right here,"" Or... ""Perfect, high five!"" That's why Your First Funnel is unlike anything you've seen before. It's truly the best program for anyone starting out online, or perhaps have never tried ClickFunnels as yet. This is the best starting point! Can this really work for MY business? I get this question a lot and my answer is always, YES! Building an online sales funnel works for any type of business in ANY industry. In other words: if you have a business or an idea to start a business, then ClickFunnels is THE software you need that can help collect new customers that become raving fans that want to give you money. It can LITERALLY be any type of business— from finance to learning how to bake cookies, to selling flashlights, to teaching people how to grow thriving gyms... Any business you want, ClickFunnels has the solution for you, and without hiring a coder, a designer, a copywriter, or a developer. As you'll soon discover in Your First Funnel's program, you can have a funnel up and running in a matter of days, if not hours. It's that easy, and that fun! What if ClickFunnels doesn't work for me? I highly doubt this will happen, seeing as ClickFunnels has been proven to work time and time again for over 106,000+ users to date. But, if you happen to fall into the .001% of people that ClickFunnels doesn't work for, then you can cancel your subscription and we'll part as friends, and you can still keep all of the free stuff on me. ;) Again, I highly doubt this will happen, especially because my team and I will be holding your hand every step of your funnel-building journey, ensuring you achieve the success you deserve. However, if after 30 days, you're not happy, then I'm not happy, and I'll do whatever it takes to make it right. Where do I start? First, go ahead and finish your form on this page and pay for 