show you how to build the confidence to ask what you're worth, how to get past those awkward situations where you need to start introducing pricing, how to help clients see the value in your programmer services, and how to close the sale - this time and every time. Module #1: Booking Qualified Appointments FAST I want to help you stop wasting your time on clients that won't convert, tire kicker is, or people who are just going to generally waste your time. You need well-qualified clients and Prospects who are willing and ready to invest money with you. In this module, I'm going to show you how to set yourself up for success by targeting the people who are most likely to invest with you, and enroll in your programs! Knowing that you were only speaking to well qualified leads will begin the process of closing with confidence. I’ll cover: The top 3 ways to collect leads for enrollment calls so you can always have a steady stream of clients Best practices for reaching out to prospective clients and customers for a call. (How often should you call? How often should you email?) How to build a customer journey that wow’s before your clients ever get on the phone and where the enrollment call falls inside of the sales process Module #2: 5 Steps to creating an irresistible offer Module 3: 5 Proven Growth Strategies for a Successful Coaching Business Once you target high quality prospects, you need to learn how to craft and deliver an irresistible offer that inspires your clients to look past price and see the true VALUE in your program. Knowing how to make a good offer that is irresistible, relatable, creates an emotional impact, WITHOUT sounding like you’re reading a sales script is NOT a natural talent. There is so much more that goes into creating a powerful offer than many people imagine, and missing the mark on this crucial aspect of your business can leave millions on the table! I will cover: Crafting Your Offer Message (Pitch) Crafting Your Offer Message (Pitch) Creating A STRONG Call To Action How to Include Your Story as Part of Your Offer How To Nail Down Your Timing ​Expert Rehearsal Strategies No more fumbling, no more uncertainty, no more anxiety, just a PERFECTLY crafted offer that will turn those “maybes” into “YES” Module #3: One-on-One Sales Conversation Outline In this module, I'm going to tell you how to craft your perfect pitch so that you can close your conversations with a successful enrollment more than 60% of the time! This is the exact same pitch and offer formula that I use to book $50,000 clients consistently, so I know it works! And truthfully, I know the best way to learn is sometimes to watch someone do it in action. That’s why I’ve had one of my top coaches role-play an enrollment call just for this purpose. The call is not scripted and will show you a great example of how your enrollment call process should proceed. You can use this for your own training materials as well! You’ll learn: How to seamlessly transition the call to discussing pricing (without it being awkward or sales pitch-y) Questions you should ask any potential client on sales calls (so you know what they’re thinking, and how to speak to their needs) ​Strong calls to action that inspire clients to enroll on the phone Examples of real-life objections and how to handle them with poise How top salespeople inspire clients to say yes Module #4: Sale Closing Outline Module 3: 5 Proven Growth Strategies for a Successful Coaching Business You’ve had a great talk with your prospective client(s), and now? Now it’s time to CLOSE. THE. SALE. Ready to learn how to convert interest into a sale or enrollment? I will show you HOW and WHEN to close the deal. How you know when it is time to close the call ​How to go from “yes, I want this” to accepting your payment What to do once the call is completed (follow ups, thanking them etc) ​​How to understand what WORKED in your call so you can use that strategy again Module #5: Addressing And Overcoming Client 