aining and will take you 60 mins to write your conversion story. But I can guarantee this time will be some of the most valuable time you'll ever spend.&nbsp; What if I'm not a confident speaker? This process will make you confident. Confidence is simply a result of practicing the right thing. Your confidence will grow faster than you can imagine. Don't let that old story stop you from sharing the gift of your story and impacting people's lives.&nbsp; Is there a 'money back satisfaction &nbsp; guarantee' &nbsp;if I don't feel it was worth the investment ? I can’t possibly imagine that happening when you see how powerful this program is. However, we are offering you a “implementation satisfaction guarantee"". If you complete the entire course within 30 days (it's around 90 mins) complete the worksheets and aren’t happy with your value, email our team [email&#160;protected] and we will refund you 100% of your $47 investment. We do not give refunds for just a change of mind. Please read terms and conditions for further details. When do I get access to the product? Instantly. It's not drip fed. You get access to all the training and templates instantly. I want you telling your story today! Okay, now let's get you sharing your signature stories with confidence. Complete the secure enrollment form and join me inside. FINAL THOUGHT: This isn’t another storytelling course. It’s a conversion system. Because likes don’t pay the bills. Claps don’t build your business. Clients do. And they’re one Conversion Story™ away from finding you. YES, COLIN! LET&#39;S DO THIS! ONLY $47?! © 2025 Boyd Coaching Pty Ltd Terms &amp; Conditions | Privacy Policy | Earnings Disclaimer | Contact This site is not part of the Meta or Instagram website or Meta Inc. or Instagram.&nbsp; Additionally, Colin Boyd &amp; this site are NOT endorsed by Meta or Instagram in any way.&nbsp; DISCLAIMER: From time to time, the Company Oxygen Consulting LLC &amp; Boyd Coaching Pty Ltd [refer to as Company] may report on the success of one of its existing or prior clients/customers. The information about this success is accurately portrayed by the Customer. You acknowledge that the prior success of others does not guarantee your success. As with any business, your results may vary and will be based on your individual capacity, business experience, expertise, and level of desire. There are no guarantees concerning the level of success you may experience. There is no guarantee that you will make any income at all and you accept the risk that the earnings and income statements differ by individual. Each individual’s success depends on his or her background, dedication, desire and motivation. The use of our information, products and services should be based on your own due diligence and you agree that the Company is not liable for any success or failure of your business that is directly or indirectly related to the purchase and use of our information, products, and services reviewed or advertised on this Website. © 2023 Oxygen Consulting LLC&nbsp;Terms &amp; Conditions | Privacy Policy | Earnings Disclaimer | Contact DISCLAIMER: Colin Boyd is not part of the Meta or Instagram website or Meta Inc. or Instagram.&nbsp; Additionally, Colin Boyd is NOT endorsed by Meta or Instagram in any way.&nbsp; Results are not typical or guaranteed."
