sp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj;&nbsp;&zwnj; View in Web Browser --> --> --> --> --> Hi Ramin, hope you're doing great! At the risk of sounding big headed: I know my programs are great. They give you a system, tools and the process for how to implement. But there's one thing my programs CAN'T do: listen to you, uncover your personal blocks that you don't even realise you have and help you overcome them right away. For that you need personal coaching. I learned this myself exactly 13 years ago and it changed my life. Have you ever met someone and within 20 seconds of talking to them you find yourself revealing stuff to them you haven't even told your family? Well...I had met this woman in Wholefoods, just randomly, because we shared a table and that's exactly what happened when she started asking me some questions. Her name was Lygya, she was Brazilian, looked incredibly young for a 60 year old...and it turned out she was a coach. We got talking and we ended up going for a walk because the conversation was so interesting. (In reality, she was giving me some free coaching just for fun) and somehow we got onto the topic of money and she goes: ""So how much money do you want to make?"" Now..at the time I was kinda broke and in debt and I'd just started my business...So after quite some thinking I say awkwardly: ""Well, I guess in a few years I'd like to make £5000 a month."" She looks at me and goes: ""Why not now?"" And I go: ""What do you mean, why not now?"" Her: ""Why not now?"" Me: ""How do you mean? I can't make £5000 now, I don't have enough going on, I don't get enough coaching work, I haven't even got subscribers yet nor an email list...I CAN'T make £5000 NOW"" And I get all worked up and defensive trying to prove to her how I totally CAN'T make £5000. She just looked at me. And then she says: ""But why can't you WANT it now?"" At this point I am just staring at her for about 30 seconds trying to understand what she means... And then...BOOM...I get it and i am having a MAJOR AHA MOMENT! All this time I've been talking about my goals like they were some distant thing in the future, sort of removed from me. But I realised for me to get excited about my goals and really take action I need to WANT to achieve them now, not in the future. I needed to feel that fire in my belly that propels me to take action NOW. Or I will never take meaningful action towards it. And the best thing? When you have a big shift your body will tell you it's happening. At that moment my tension disappeared, my voice dropped about an octave and my breathing went about twice as deep. All because of a powerful coaching intervention. (And honestly speaking it's those moments when you notice your client having a big AHA moment is one of the best feelings in the world!) So that's what good coaching can do. When they talk about ""unlocking potential""...that's literally what she did with me then. And if you've read all the way until here I am pretty sure you already know how powerful coaching could be for you. There really is no substitute for having someone in your corner, challenging you to be your best and holding you accountable. And in the process helping you to sidestep those internal blocks. For a few days only I accept new coaching clients. It will be me personally (not some team member) who is going to be help you achieve your goals. You'll have me in your corner, 100%, rooting for you, helping you remove the blocks, removing the brain fog and helping you move forward with momentum. If you can see yourself changing your life with my help... secure your spot here If you have questions hit reply and ask. But...don't delay. :-) Laters, Stephan --> --> Unsubscribe | Sent by Stephan Erdman Ltd Park Road &bull; London, London &bull; SE25"
https://fortuneacademy.co.uk/,Course (Paid) (Bunisess),"Fortune Academy UK: Offers trading and financial education courses in the UK, focusing on forex, stock market trading, and personal wealth management strategies.",Fortune Academy | Mindset Before Money,Hither Mann - Fast Track Forex has been dubbed the world&#039;s best trading system for beginners. Welcome to the World’s First Lifetime Wealth Coaching Academy.,"WELCOME TO THE WORLD&#8217;S FIRST LIFETIME WEALTH COACHING ACADEMY&nbsp;, Hither Mann is also known as the &#8220;Millionaire Mentor&#8221; to HNW, UHNW individuals and businesses by Luxury Magazine, Monaco, Mayfair, Miami and Moscow., IS FORTUNE ACADEMY FOR YOU?, , ","Fortune Academy | Mindset Before Money Facebook Twitter Youtube Linkedin Instagram Home OUR TRAINING COURSES Free Forex Training Fast Track Forex Fast Track Business Millionaire Mindset Program The Billionaire Project Student Testimonials Fast Track Forex Testimonials Contact Us JOIN ME AT MY NEXT EVENT WELCOME TO THE WORLD&#8217;S FIRST LIFETIME WEALTH COACHING ACADEMY&nbsp; &nbsp; THE WORLD&#8217;S FIRST FEMALE TRADER, INTERNATIONAL SPEAKER &amp; TRAINER, HITHER MANN (FOUNDER &amp; CEO). HITHER IS ALSO PEAK PERFORMANCE COACH TO PRIVATE WEALTH BANKERS AT &nbsp; &nbsp; AS SEEN ON: Hither Mann is also known as the &#8220;Millionaire Mentor&#8221; to HNW, UHNW individuals and businesses by Luxury Magazine, Monaco, Mayfair, Miami and Moscow. &#8220;I grew up in a traditional&nbsp;household where there were many money&nbsp;problems and I knew from the age of 9 I was going to be super wealthy one day to help my parents out of their difficulties! I was told by everyone growing up that &#8220;school and university&nbsp;education&#8221; was all I needed to be wealthy. I aced every exam only to find out they were wrong. Formal education gave me a career I felt&nbsp;trapped in. It was after 2004, once I discovered property networking groups and other &#8220;wealth education seminars&#8221; where I began learning the real wealth building skills in life and business! My mission now is to help as many others see the truth behind mastering wealth creation. That is the legacy I wish to leave behind. Many people are wasting lives chasing money, forgetting that when we die we take none of it with us. Thus the real enjoyment in life can come when money is no longer a source of anxiety and you can live freely on your terms alone. My Mental&nbsp;Health Charity&nbsp; &#8220;The Fortune Family Foundation&#8221; is set up to educate those in a working&nbsp;environment to end the anxiety around money problems. Fortune Academy is my platform to sound my philosophies and teachings and to create the legacy that is far bigger than life alone. LEARN MORE ABOUT HITHER IS FORTUNE ACADEMY FOR YOU? Fortune Academy&#8217;s signature is&nbsp;the #mindsetbeforemoney approach. Without the &#8220;Millionaire Mindset&#8221; &nbsp;you cannot create&nbsp;sustainable wealth in any industry. Thus every&nbsp; mentorship&nbsp;training you&nbsp;receive by Hither Mann and the Fortune Academy&nbsp;trainers will incorporate a very strong approach on mindset over all else.&nbsp; To shift your mindset from a &#8220;9-5&#8221; thinker to an &#8220;investor&#8221; takes a considerably long time hence the lifetime mentorship we offer. We know Rome wasn&#8217;t built in a day and thus we want students who will commit to all their training for a minimum of 3 years! Hither conducts training via The Millionaire Mindset Program and the Forex Training Courses. Crypto Trading and E-Commerce strategies are taught by separate trainers. Fortune Academy is the world&#8217;s first LIFETIME wealth education provider. It has taught over 25,000 students since 2016 and has successfully created profitable traders, business owners and investors in many industries. See the Student Testimonials &nbsp;section at the top of the home page for more information. Fortune Academy events are held primarily in London where people from all over the world travel to benefit from the wealth education provided by Hither Mann and her &#8220;Fortune Family&#8221;. Make sure you visit the events page to register for the next London event to learn the areas we cover from The Millionaire Mindset Program , Financial Trading , Cryptocurrency and Online Business programs via Ecommerce. The EXECUTIVE branch of Fortune Academy focusses on Institutional business from IPOs and Private Equity Ventures as well as FinTech companies. Hither offers these events as &#8216;invite-only&#8221; events to a select UHNW audience. Learn more about all the above at the events in London! JOIN ME AT MY NEXT EVENT IMPERSONATOR ACCOUNTS There are many FAKE profiles on social media that impersonate Hither Mann and Fortune Academy which will entice you to give your money to them for either &#8220;bitcoin mining&#8221; or other &#8220;manage forex accounts&#8221;. This is STRICTLY AGAINST Fortune Academy policies and we do NOT take deposits from anyone to trade your money or for bitcoin/crypto mining. Fortune Academy is an EDUCATION ONLY service which will teach you how to trade your OWN money and we will never take your money for investment into financial services or brokerage accounts! FORTUNE ACADEMY IS NOT A BROKERAGE EITHER, we do not get paid or incentivised by a broker through our financial education services. Fortune Academy only offers it&#8217;s services through an event (webinar/workshop) with Hither Mann herself where she carefully selects the students she works with under her lifetime education service! Please stay clear and report all profiles who impersonate Hither or Fortune Academy. Hither Mann&#8217;s social media links are always @hithermann and there are no other associated accounts that she operates. Please CLICK HERE to verify the social media profiles she uses. Be safe and we wish you SUCCESS in your financial journey always! Love Hither x &nbsp; JOIN ME AT MY NEXT EVENT © 2023 Fortune Academy | All Rights Reserved | Privacy Policy | Terms &amp; Conditions"
