https://www.productside.com/courses-overview/?utm_campaign=PM%20Day%202024&utm_medium=email&_hsenc=p2ANqtz-8tLmhCfwT3b7G76svFVi_-IJn9Yk2rdLPU-3Dk_0xQJySXJ5ld9sIR5cBirteYVcvimPKfYzfRampML1Z63LE5Wh8euA&_hsmi=306379644&utm_content=306379644&utm_source=hs_email,Course (Paid) (Bunisess),"Product Side Courses Overview: A landing page offering overviews of courses related to product management, designed to enhance skills and knowledge in product development and strategy.",Product Management Certification &amp; Courses &amp; Training,"Advance your career with our Product Management Certification, Courses, and Training. Learn key skills to excel in product management and drive business success.","Product Management Certification &#8211; Courses, Upskill. Get Certified. Become Invaluable., Choose Your Path to Success, Optimal Product Management, AI Product Management, Digital Product Management, Agile Product Management, Why Get Trained by Productside?, Real Results from Real Experts, Templates and Tools You Can Use, Small Class Sizes, Big Impact, Learning on Your Terms, What Do Our Graduates Say?, Kimberly Johnson, Chris Barylski, Eric Haar, Danielle Chapleau, Patrick Perl, Jennifer Temple, Alexander Rojinski, Chris Frandsen, Krasimir Dimitrov, Nicole Torrillo, Mike Freier, Sara Athanas, William Campbell, Step 1  |  Launch Your Product Management Career, Step 2  |  Accelerate to Senior Product Manager, Step 3  |  Lead with Confidence as a Product Management Expert, Want Private Training?, Resources, Support","Product Management Certification &amp; Courses &amp; Training Skip to content Blueprint Your Product Management Playbooks Courses Optimal Product Management Training Agile Product Management Training AI Product Management Training Digital Product Management Training AIPMM Product Management Certification Corporate Training Team Custom Training Executive Leadership Workshop Product Management Collaboration Consulting Diagnostic – Product Management Maturity Assessments Team Assessments Individual Skills Assessment Advisory Resources Tools + Templates Success Stories Webinars Blog Podcasts About Us Learner Login Blueprint Your Product Management Playbooks Courses Optimal Product Management Training Agile Product Management Training AI Product Management Training Digital Product Management Training AIPMM Product Management Certification Corporate Training Team Custom Training Executive Leadership Workshop Product Management Collaboration Consulting Diagnostic – Product Management Maturity Assessments Team Assessments Individual Skills Assessment Advisory Resources Tools + Templates Success Stories Webinars Blog Podcasts About Us Learner Login GET IN TOUCH Cart &#36; 0.00 Product Management Certification &#8211; Courses Upskill. Get Certified. Become Invaluable. Step into product management certification confidently. Lead more effectively as a senior PM. Join the 86% of certified PMs who report improved team alignment and business outcomes. Choose Your Path to Success Optimal Product Management Master the core skills of product management, from discovery to delivery. Build strategies that align with customer needs – profitably. Perfect for: PMs who want to strengthen their end-to-end product skills. Learn More AI Product Management Design AI-driven products that deliver real business impact while using AI tools to streamline your day-to-day PM workflows. Perfect for: PMs who want to drive innovation and build smarter AI-powered solutions. Learn More Digital Product Management Apply design thinking, rapid experimentation, and data-driven strategies to build and scale. Perfect for: PMs leading digital transformation for physical products or enhancing digital experiences. Learn More Agile Product Management Lead your team effectively in high-speed environments. Master agile practices. Keep your roadmaps adaptable. Perfect for: PMs driving cross-functional collaboration and continuous delivery in fast-paced markets. Learn More Why Get Trained by Productside? Real Results from Real Experts Led by experts from Amazon, Microsoft, and Honeywell, our instructors combine real-world experience with a passion for mentorship, equipping you with PM plays you can use from day one. Templates and Tools You Can Use The Optimal Product Management course includes the Productside Playbook™—22 templates covering every stage of the product lifecycle. Other courses offer tailored frameworks and tools you can apply right away. Small Class Sizes, Big Impact Learn in an engaging environment with less than 20 participants per class. More interaction. More insights. Better results. Learning on Your Terms Live Online Interactive, instructor-led sessions with real-time feedback and peer collaboration. Self-Study Go at your own pace with on-demand content and hands-on exercises. In-Person Immerse yourself in an engaging, distraction-free learning experience. What Do Our Graduates Say? Don’t just take our word for it – see what product professionals have to say Kimberly Johnson Product Manager at The Home Depot “I enjoyed the continuous learning and feedback. Being in a small group allowed us to be more interactive. This was the best business class I’ve had in a long time.” Chris Barylski Product Manager at Otava “I would absolutely recommend that anyone either thinking about moving into the product management field or new to product management, take a look at Productside and the Optimal Product Management course.” Eric Haar Transition Specialist at CreativeOne “The best part of training were the trainer’s stories, which really helped frame the content, and the group breakouts, which really helped solidify the concepts in a concrete way.” Danielle Chapleau Product Supply Manager at Card Kingdom “I got everything I needed out of the class. I feel ready and prepared to take on my role with more context into how I should be approaching new and retiring products.” Patrick Perl Customer Experience Leadership at H&amp;R Block “The course highlighted that AI products should be focused on solving a problem, not just reducing expenses.”​ Jennifer Temple Sr. Pricing Product Manager at RingCentral “I got way more out of this class than I was expecting in how to apply Agile principles in my day job and communicate more effectively with stakeholders.” Alexander Rojinski Product Manager at Transplant Connect ""Taking the course was like completing a mini-MBA but focused entirely on Product Management and the Product Lifecycle."" Chris Frandsen CEO at AIPMM “The Optimal Product Management course is well-structured and easy to navigate, making it perfect for busy professionals. I could easily fit in a module during lunch or a short break.” Krasimir Dimitrov PO/PM/Senior BA at Astea “The launch readiness content is extremely relevant and valuable, providing techniques that can be directly applied to real-world scenarios.” Nicole Torrillo UCaaS Product Manager at Northland Communications “I really like the resource templates provided. They explain the steps well, and the problem statement template makes defining the problem easier!” Mike Freier Principal and Lead Consultant Principal and Lead Consultant at Product Management Consulting Group Inc. “The AI course gave me hands-on experience with advanced prompting and buyer personas, which I can directly apply in my day-to-day work to improve market intelligence and storytelling. ” Sara Athanas Digital Services Executive at Vodafone “The Productside Blueprint provided a fresh perspective, emphasizing the importance of a customer-centric approach in product development.” William Campbell Head of Design at Actionstep ""“Roger is AWESOME. From his own war stories, to his ability to involve everyone, give time for questions and clarifications by giving more examples. Truly impressive.”"" Step 1 | Launch Your Product Management Career Start strong with personalized tools and certifications designed to help you land your first role. Build your skills roadmap with our free assessment tool. Take the Optimal Product Management course to master the fundamentals and gain a globally recognized certification. Gain industry-recognized certifications to stand out on LinkedIn. Explore practical resources to navigate your first PM role with confidence. Start Your Free Assessment Step 2 | Accelerate to Senior Product Manager Ready to grow? Deepen your expertise and lead with impact. Create a strategic career plan with our Career Planning Template. Master AI tools and strategies with the AI Product Management course. Lead Agile teams and drive delivery with the Agile Product Management course. Scale SaaS products and boost revenue with Digital Product Management training. Explore Courses Step 3 | Lead with Confidence as a Product Management Expert Become the leader your team looks to for direction and success. Download our Leadership Pack and guide your team to excellence. Use the Productside Blueprint™ to refine your product processes. Align your team with actionable insights from our Team Assessment. Partner with us to build your dream team through customized training. Lead Towards Outcomes Want Private Training? Tailored courses for your team, designed to solve your unique challenges. Perfect for teams of 8 or more. Let&#039;s Talk Subscribe To Our Newsletter Join our newsletter and stay up to date with all things current and Product Management related. Resources Blog Webinars Podcast Tools + Templates Blog Webinars Podcast Tools + Templates Support FAQ Careers Contact Us | Help and Support FAQ Careers Contact Us | Help and Support Facebook X-twitter Youtube Linkedin Instagram Privacy Policy Terms &#038; Conditions Privacy Policy Terms &#038; Conditions © 2025 Productside. All rights reserved. Go to Top Blueprint Your Product Management Playbooks Courses Optimal Product Management Training Agile Product Management Training AI Product Management Training Digital Product Management Training AIPMM Product Management Certification Corporate Training Team Custom Training Executive Leadership Workshop Product Management Collaboration Consulting Diagnostic – Product Management Maturity Assessments Team Assessments Individual Skills Assessment Advisory Resources Tools + Templates Success Stories Webinars Blog Podcasts About Us Learner Login GET IN TOUCH Clear Search Shopping cart Your cart is empty Subtotal Continue shopping View cart Checkout"
