u don't know what to say, or if you blank out, or if you doubt yourself. [00:03:20] TEST: Is this masterclass for you? [00:04:41] Find out how David went from invisible to interesting himself, his path to overcoming all the wrong advice out there, to finally understanding the five invisible to interesting principles. [00:05:58] The three secrets to having amazing conversations without having an adventurous life or the need to be an extrovert. [00:06:28] How to become someone interesting and engaging to talk to even if you think people aren't interested in what you have to say. [00:06:39] How to use the Wing Strokes principle to signal that you are interested and engaged in the conversation without looking needy. [00:12:29] Learn to use Dynamic Conversations to never run out of things to say. [00:15:20] The secret to socializing less and making more friends with people you find naturally in social life situations without having born a charismatic person. [00:17:39] Discover how to form meaningful relations without being a loud extrovert. [00:19:23] The Invisible to Interesting member Brandon tells how the principles helped him to overcome his brain’s excuses not to act when he was afraid of failure and rejection. [00:22:33] The power of the Invisible to Interesting Framework as a structured approach with real-life applications that can transform a person’s social life, with practical ways to engage, connect, and form bonds with others. [00:28:28] Discover the amazing bonuses that will make you go through this path to transform your social life much faster. [00:29:10] Access a community of like-minded people to help you in your journey from Invisible to Interestingwith easy-to-understand video lessons, footage from real-life interactions, and exercises that will 10X how fast you improve. [00:30:16] A couple more case studies from Invisible to Interesting members who felt too depressed to make friends, or who found a lot of support in the Social Self community to overcome their social struggles. [00:30:45] Unique opportunity: Peek inside the program Invisible to Interesting and learn how you can try it out risk-free (only available on this page). About David Morin David A. Morin featured in Entrepreneur Magazine Hi! I’m David, founder of SocialSelf. When my middle school peers went to school discos, I was at home building model cars. As I grew older I felt clueless about how to talk to people. I had some friendships through school, but sometimes they were one-sided and other times toxic. As an adult I spent lots of weekends alone and the thought of socializing made me anxious. I felt like I bored people. I got stuck in small talk. I got ignored in groups. And at the same time, I didn’t want to turn into one of those over-extroverted “partygoers” that I associated with socializing. Out of pure luck, I got to know really socially savvy people that I actually liked. I studied what they did and realized that you don’t have to be loud and obnoxious or shallow to have a great social life. You can build close friendships and even enjoy meeting new people &#8211; while being yourself more than ever! When I started figuring this out, people began asking me for advice. And that’s how SocialSelf started, over 12 years ago! It’s so cool to get out of bed every morning and read emails from people who thank us for their new, more fulfilling social lives. And if this program makes a big change in your life too, I‘d be so happy to hear from you! Read More Please do not close this page as this offer is only available here. As a reward for watching this masterclass, you have unlocked a special offer for this program. Go From Invisible to Interesting Become a captivating person and connect with anyone, even if you doubt yourself, don’t know what to say, or perhaps just feel bland Carry Engaging Conversations with Anyone - In Only 10 Minutes Per Day In only 10 minutes a day from the comfort of your home, Invisible to Interesting shows you how to carry engaging and interesting conversations with anyone. Is self-doubt holding you back from connecting with people? Interesting people set themselves apart by turning everyday topics into exciting conversations. They, just like anyone, can experience self-doubt. They’ve just figured out how to not let their self-doubt hold them back. That’s why breaking free from self-doubt is the first step to become a more memorable you. Do you run out of things to say? Anxiety tends to make us filter ourselves too hard so it feels like we never have anything to say. But it’s not as easy as removing the filter, because what if you then end up saying something irrelevant, offensive, or embarrassing? Becoming engaging and memorable isn’t as easy as just talking more. It’s about knowing how to connect and set yourself apart. You don’t need to be extroverted, loud, witty, or have an amazing life, to be a memorable person I used to believe I had to have more hobbies, travel more, or just be more confident to connect with people. In reality, I just didn’t know what to talk about to move my conversations forward. With Invisible to Interesting, you’ll learn to take any mundane conversation and turn it into an opportunity for you to connect and set yourself apart. When you know how to do it, it’s quite easy. When others see you do it, it looks like magic. This helps you connect: With coworkers With a date With anyone you run into About David Morin David A. Morin featured in Entrepreneur Magazine Hi! I’m David, founder of SocialSelf. When my middle school peers went to school discos, I was at home building model cars. As I grew older I felt clueless about how to talk to people. I had some friendships through school, but sometimes they were one-sided and other times toxic. As an adult I spent lots of weekends alone and the thought of socializing made me anxious. I felt like I bored people. I got stuck in small talk. I got ignored in groups. And at the same time, I didn’t want to turn into one of those over-extroverted “partygoers” that I associated with socializing. Out of pure luck, I got to know really socially savvy people that I actually liked. I studied what they did and realized that you don’t have to be loud and obnoxious or shallow to have a great social life. You can build close friendships and even enjoy meeting new people &#8211; while being yourself more than ever! When I started figuring this out, people began asking me for advice. And that’s how SocialSelf started, over 12 years ago! It’s so cool to get out of bed every morning and read emails from people who thank us for their new, more fulfilling social lives. And if this program makes a big change in your life too, I‘d be so happy to hear from you! Read More This program is for you if: You get the feeling people aren’t interested in you You often don’t know what to say or talk about You feel invisible in groups Socializing overwhelms you and you are held back by self-doubt Friends or dates often seem to to lose interest You struggle to find a way to set yourself apart 79% Report an increase in self-confidence 82% Report an increase in social skills 80% Report improvement in their social anxiety *According to a survey of 819 SocialSelf members Introducing Invisible to Interesting Grow your conversation skills from home, at your own pace, so that when you talk to people, you&#8217;ll intuitively know what to . Learn to make conversation in a captivating way (without the need for spectacular experiences or topics) Break out of old conditioning from parents and bullies that is holding you back Talk with anyone, whether it’s someone you’re attracted to or a group of people. Break through shallow small talk so you can build real connections fast. Highlights Day by day Part 1 Building a captivating persona Hide breakdown With the help of simulated conversations you rewire your brain to talk to people with confidence. You develop the ability to intuitively know what to say to move the converation forward, maintain interest, and build real connections with strangers, co-workers, friends, and dates. Topics include: Create engaging, interesting, confident conversations using the “attentional-shift” method. Bypass the part of your brain that makes you feel self-conscious Leverage what the other person says as an infinite source of conversation topics Secure permanent, life-long results And much more Day 1 The cues that make people interesting Day 2 Why some become interesting and others not Day 3 The principles that make you interesting to talk to Day 4 The Engage-Method Day 5 Hidden pitfalls where most people fail Part 2 Conveying who you are in an engaging and interesting way Show breakdown You will get the tools needed to become interesting and memorable in group settings while staying true to yourself. Learn skills to be interesting right off the bat with the Dribble &amp; Pass Strategies to set yourself apart without changing who you are Methods to take initiative Signaling friendliness And much more Day 6 The Dribble &amp; Pass Day 7 Taking initiative Day 8 Signaling friendliness Part 3 Bypassing the small talk barrier Show breakdown Techniques to know what to say in any conversation Exercises to prevent blanking out How to hold a listener&#8217;s interest Methods to turn painful small talk into meaningful discussions Techniques for engaging conversations Principles to find common ground with anyone And much more Day 9 The hidden power behind sharing your thoughts Day 10 Talking more &amp; an example conversation Day 11 The skill of elaborating Day 12 Moving past small talk: Part 1 Day 13 Exercise: The association game Day 14 Moving past small talk: Part 2 Day 15 Exercise: The two explorers Part 4 Deeper connections Show breakdown Strategies to maintain and grow friendships over time Techniques to overcome fears of getting closer Exercises to build trust and mutual understanding Using the the Lighthouse Principle for lifelong connections And much more Day 16 Daring to be personal Day 17 Techniques to overcome fears of opening up Day 18 Exercise: Sharing thoughts Day 19 Finding the balance in how much to share Day 20 The Lighthouse Principle Day 21 Controversial opinions and disagreements Part 5 Breaking barriers to social success Show breakdown This module will assist you in overcoming the last obstacles to effective communication, preparing you for social success. Techniques for handling controversial topics and bragging Strategies to avoid the listener&#8217;s trap Exercises to overcome fears and perceived shortcomings Methods to clear roadblocks to successful communication And much more Day 22 Talking about things you don’t know anything about Day 23 Subconscious bragging Day 24 Getting unstuck from the listener’s trap Day 25 Reprogramming the feeling that you’ll bore people Day 26 Moving forward Bonus 1 Conversation Confidence Bonus 2 Invisible to Interesting: The Game Bonus 3 Conversation Scripts Word-for-Word Bonus 4 Social Self Inner Circle Bonus 5 Instantly More Likable Part 2 Energy Awareness &amp; Personal Presence Show breakdown You’ll discover how to instantly Boost Your Personal Presence — so you can be more confident, comfortable and attentive in ANY situation. As you become more present, you’ll start to feel calmer and clarity in your life… with plenty of time and energy to make your deepest goals a reality. In this session, you’ll discover how to anchor your Root Chakra to the center of the earth and learn a simple yet powerful energy focusing technique called “Looking From Behind Your Eyes” — both of which will help you instantly get present whenever you choose. Topics include: The Power of Energy Awareness &amp; Healing Your Body-Spirit Connection for Personal Presence Deepening Your Grounding &amp; Personal Presence How to Practice Personal Presence Meditations include: Personal Presence Meditation (Daily Meditation) Advanced Meditation — Getting Into Your Body Advanced Guided Journey — Center of the Earth Are You Intuitive? What Is Intuition? Release Blocks To Intuition Energy Tools To Improve Your Intuition Intuition: How To Find Direction & Timing Intuition: Exercises & Applications Using Your Intuition: Self-Practice Day --> Yes! I'm ready to register! Become a captivating person faster with these bonuses Bonus 1 Build your conversation abilities with Invisible to Interesting: The Game (Worth $349) Becoma a master conversationalist and go all the way from “hi” to becoming friends. You improve your conversation skills while playing this game in the comfort of your home – without even having to talk to strangers. Bonus 2 Never run out of things to say with Conversation Scripts Word for Word (Worth $196) Ever wished you just had a script for what to say? This is it. This is our step-by-step system to make conversation with anyone. Learn how to get past the small talk, avoid awkward silence, and connect by making conversation. Bonus 3 Build confidence from within with Conversation Confidence (Worth $395) Neuroscience has given us a new way to develop unbreakable core confidence. This program will make you more confident in social settings by turning off that annoying “What will people think of me?”-alarm. Bonus 4 Click with people faster with Instantly More Likable (Worth $987) During 1.5 years time, we developed a framework that anyone can apply to become a truly likable individual – withouth having to turn into someone else or become a people pleaser. Instantly More Likable is a full length program that will help you become a truly likable person. Bonus 5 Get lifetime access to everything (Worth $987) When signing up for this unique package, you’re getting lifetime access to Invisible to Interesting, Invisible to Interesting: The Game, Conversation Scripts Word-for-Word, Conversation Confidence, AND Instantly More Likable. This means that you’ll have access to all these courses and all future updates to them for the rest of your life. Bonus 1 Maximize your spiritual fitness with Unlocking Transcendence (worth $299) Unlocking Transcendence with Jeffrey Allen is a systematic, fun, step-by-step journey of self-awareness and a remarkable roadmap to spiritual fitness. You’ll go far beyond regular spiritual practices like meditation and prayer - and embody advanced spiritual skills that keep you beautifully and perpetually aligned with your highest purpose. Bonus 1 Maximize your spiritual fitness with Unlocking Transcendence (worth $299) Unlocking Transcendence with Jeffrey Allen is a systematic, fun, step-by-step journey of self-awareness and a remarkable roadmap to spiritual fitness. You’ll go far beyond regular spiritual practices like meditation and prayer - and embody advanced spiritual skills that keep you beautifully and perpetually aligned with your highest purpose. --> Yes! I'm ready to register! Try it For 15 Days Risk Free No need to say YES right now. Just say MAYBE. Go through the materials for 15 days risk-free from the day of purchase. No emails, no phone calls, no hassle. Just click Refund on your account page and get a full, friendly and fast refund. No questions asked. What's included: &#10003; Invisible to Interesting $899 &#10003; Invisible to Interesting: The Game $349 &#10003; Conversation Scripts $196 &#10003; Social Self Inner Circle $949 &#10003; Lifetime Access to All Updates $987 &#10003; Instantly More Likable $987 &#10003; TOTAL VALUE $4,367 You Get All This What’s included in your program: Lifetime access to the course. 29+ super in-depth, easy to understand videos packed with ultra-practical real-world examples. A community of like-minded who’ll support you and understand you. Exercises that help you intuitively know what to do when you&#8217;re actually talking to someone. A system that holds you accountable and motivated. Downloadable audio files of the lessons so that you can listen anywhere on your phone. 15-day money-back guarantee: If you don’t become a more interesting person who can