https://www.toastmasters.org/Find-a-Club/06787373-london-toastmasters,Course (Paid) (Self help),London Toastmasters provides a platform for individuals to improve their public speaking and leadership skills through structured programs and peer feedback​ (WisLibrary)​.,Toastmasters International -London Toastmasters,"Toastmasters International is a nonprofit educational organization that builds confidence and teaches public speaking skills through a worldwide network of clubs that meet online and in person. In a supportive community or corporate environment, members prepare and deliver speeches, respond to impromptu questions, and give and receive constructive feedback. It is through this regular practice that members are empowered to meet personal and professional communication goals. Founded in 1924, the organization is headquartered in Englewood, Colorado with over 270,000 members in more than 14,000 clubs in 150 countries.","London Toastmasters, What to expect with your free club visit, Loading...","Toastmasters International -London Toastmasters Skip to main content Menu WHERE LEADERS ARE MADE Login Find a Club Start a Club Contact Us My Home My Profile Toggle Search Search Search Find a Club About Education Programs Membership Resources Magazine Events Shop Home / Find a Club / London Toastmasters London Toastmasters Club meets: Tuesday (2nd &amp; 4th of the Month),&nbsp;6:30 PM London Toastmasters Club Number: 06787373,&nbsp;91,&nbsp;Area&nbsp;L23 Charter Date: Mar. 8, 2018 Visit This Website Contact/visit club Club Information Meeting Times: Tuesday (2nd &amp; 4th of the Month)&nbsp;6:30 PM Location: Haddon Hall 157 Tower Bridge Road, London SE1 3LW 22 Tower Bridge Road London,&nbsp;&nbsp;SE1 4TR &nbsp;United Kingdom Membership Restriction: None; the club is open to all interested parties. Get directions What to expect with your free club visit When you visit a Toastmasters club as a guest, there&rsquo;s no pressure to participate until you are ready and comfortable. Every club is unique; visit as many clubs as you would like to find the right fit for you! Other clubs in the area Search Search City of London Toastmasters Club London ,&nbsp;United Kingdom Meeting Time: Doors open 6:15pm. Meeting Starts 6:30pm, 1st, 3rd &amp; 5th Tuesday Berkeley Square Speakers Toastmasters Club London ,&nbsp;United Kingdom Meeting Time: 7.30 am - 8.45 am, Wednesdays Loading... FAQ | Privacy Policy | Conditions of Use | Browser Compatibility | Copyright | Media Center | Careers © 2025 Toastmasters International. &nbsp;All rights reserved. Toastmasters International Find a Club Start a Club Login Search Search"
https://www.philipattar.com/codesofconsciousness,Course (Paid) (Self help),"Philip Attar's Codes of Consciousness: Likely a spiritual or personal development website offering insights, courses, or resources on expanding consciousness.",,Philip &amp; Amanda-Lee Attar&#39;s Living Immersion Method™ 🧬 Unlock the DNA Intelligence of Your Highest Potential,", Living Immersion™Unlock the DNA Intelligence of Your Highest Potential in Purpose &amp; Sacred Union, , This is NOT mindset coaching.This is NOT traditional meditation.This is NOT breathwork.This is NOT therapy., This is a distilled and effective somatic energy method to clearly see where you're getting stuck, so you can dissolve the ripple of generational conditioning holding you back from embodying your greater purpose as a conscious leader, entrepreneur, or healing practitioner.This path is for you if you've caught yourself in an unproductive cycle of perpetual 'healing' losing valuable energy and time. You're ready to leave behind your healing stage and motivate greater career growth with more clarity, focus, and drive., Testimonials:, ""Throw away any ideas of what meditation or therapy might be. Throw away any sense of expectation. Understand that you are doing something quite daunting in recalibrating how you actually live. If you do that, the joys you can experience in this are unprecedented and unlimited."", — Selema Masekela, Sports Media Personality, Entrepreneur, ""We are accessing something so true, so eternal, and finally in a way where it is not just glimpsed but embodied and radiated in a sustainable way..."", — Lisa B., Executive Coach, ""I always believed my next levels in life would be reached through mastering my mind. But I was hitting tons of unconscious resistance in this pursuit. The next levels of expansion are not through use of the mind, but in reducing the ripple of friction and conditioning that was clouding my highest divine destiny.The Living Immersion Method reveals how to tap into divine flow, feeling it, merging with it, embodying it to make clearer, higher choices while I step into the unknown.LIM is the most self empowering, expansive ""method"" I have ever witnessed. It is your next step.""— John Graham / 3 x USA Memory Champion, ""If I had to pinpoint one thing here it's that I was able to be present with whatever challenge or decision was in front of me and instead of solely logically thinking my way through the choice, it's as if I now tap into a greater perspective where I can see the next best step and feel with every cell of my being that it's the next step to take.It's very empowering. It amazes me how simple and effective this is. I've done everything from Vipassana to Joe Dispenza to all kinds of personal growth work and this is the most useful. It's kind of like the minimalist approach to cosmic consciousness.""— Jeff A. / Business &amp; Performance Mindset Coach, , Sign up and join thousands of visionary leaders in our free weekly newsletter, Instagram: @philipattar, With 100,000+ followers, follow my wife Amanda-Lee and I on Instagram for daily posts and videos on our Living Immersion Method™, notes on consciousness, and advanced energy somatic practices to help you embody your highest potential., Two Step, Sign up for updates on events, workshops,&nbsp;notes on consciousness and healing.","Philip Attar philipattar.com is now academyoflivingintelligence.com Academy of Living Intelligence Private 1:1: Union Living Immersion Academy About Login Living Immersion™ Unlock the DNA Intelligence of Your Highest Potential in Purpose &amp; Sacred Union This is NOT mindset coaching. This is NOT traditional meditation. This is NOT breathwork. This is NOT therapy. This is a distilled and effective somatic energy method to clearly see where you're getting stuck, so you can dissolve the ripple of generational conditioning holding you back from embodying your greater purpose as a conscious leader, entrepreneur, or healing practitioner. This path is for you if you've caught yourself in an unproductive cycle of perpetual 'healing' losing valuable energy and time. You're ready to leave behind your healing stage and motivate greater career growth with more clarity, focus, and drive. Testimonials: "" Throw away any ideas of what meditation or therapy might be. Throw away any sense of expectation. Understand that you are doing something quite daunting in recalibrating how you actually live. If you do that, t he joys you can experience in this are unprecedented and unlimited."" — Selema Masekela, Sports Media Personality, Entrepreneur ""We are accessing something so true, so eternal, and finally in a way where it is not just glimpsed but embodied and radiated in a sustainable way..."" — Lisa B., Executive Coach "" I always believed my next levels in life would be reached through mastering my mind. But I was hitting tons of unconscious resistance in this pursuit. The next levels of expansion are not through use of the mind, but in reducing the ripple of friction and conditioning that was clouding my highest divine destiny. The Living Immersion Method reveals how to tap into divine flow, feeling it, merging with it, embodying it to make clearer, higher choices while I step into the unknown. LIM is the most self empowering, expansive ""method"" I have ever witnessed. It is your next step."" — John Graham / 3 x USA Memory Champion "" If I had to pinpoint one thing here it's that I was able to be present with whatever challenge or decision was in front of me and instead of solely logically thinking my way through the choice, it's as if I now tap into a greater perspective where I can see the next best step and feel with every cell of my being that it's the next step to take. It's very empowering. It amazes me how simple and effective this is. I've done everything from Vipassana to Joe Dispenza to all kinds of personal growth work and this is the most useful. It's kind of like the minimalist approach to cosmic consciousness."" — Jeff A. / Business &amp; Performance Mindset Coach Sign up and join thousands of visionary leaders in our free weekly newsletter Social media as you know is not permanent, not private, and not the best way to stay intimately connected. Every week discover how to heal the relationship wounds holding your conscious business back from God-led purpose & impact. SIGN ME UP! Instagram: @philipattar With 100,000+ followers, follow my wife Amanda-Lee and I on Instagram for daily posts and videos on our Living Immersion Method™, notes on consciousness, and advanced energy somatic practices to help you embody your highest potential. FOLLOW US EMBODIED TRUTH &copy; 2025 Philip Attar Creative LLC Powered by Kajabi Newsletter Program Terms of Use Website Terms Privacy Contact Close 50% Complete Two Step Sign up for updates on events, workshops,&nbsp; notes on consciousness and healing. SUBMIT"
