Partners are Human pack. So far me and my partner have gotten to know so many special things about each other because the cards spark up new conversations in our decade old relationship. A Alison Fun and makes my family slow down and appreciate life I Innthee Aroonsuck (Portland, OR) An Amazing Connecting Resource I highly recommend this card game to anyone who is interested in connecting or reconnecting with their families. While I purchased the Thai to English version to connect with my mother, I have played this game with my English speaking partner and other family members, as well. The game is incredibly versatile and sparks conversations beyond its initial prompts; it has been an investment into my family's well-being and mental health! A Anh-Nguyet Tried at Christmas with grandma and it was fun and a learning experience to see how everyone reacted - and their response to her. A Ashley Yeung (San Jose, CA) Great bonding activity I loved this game! I felt like I learned so much about my parents and got them to tell me stories that I otherwise would not have asked them about. This game reminds me of We’re Not Really Strangers but it’s focused more on how you connect with your parents which I appreciated. 5 stars!!!!! E Eliza Dunn (El Centro, CA) Great way to reconnect with older family members I bought these cards before visiting my elderly uncle. It was a fun way to get reacquainted and record some great memories. Thanks for creating these! 1 2 3 Frequently Asked Questions How long will shipping take? We ship all orders within 24 hours of your purchase; same-day if ordered by 3 pm PT Mon-Sat. 📦 Domestic orders within the United States typically arrive within 1-5 days of shipping (depending how far you are from where we ship—San Francisco, CA), with many faster options available at checkout. 💡 Enter your shipping address at checkout for an estimated delivery date! Orders outside the US usually arrive within 1-3 weeks. Free shipping in the US with 2+ products 🇺🇸 Free shipping to Canada with 2+ products 🇨🇦 Flat rate global shipping 🌏 Every order is hand-packed by my Mom & Dad then delivered to the post office with the utmost love and care. 🫶 How accurate are your translations? Instead of relying on a single translator, company, or service, we work with ~10 native speakers on average along with their loved ones to meticulously trans-create each card from English into another language. This process takes a minimum of 6-8 months per language, with hundreds of combined hours spent to ensure that the nuances of each language are honored, that people from every relevant & major geographic location review the translations to make sure locals can understand, and every detail like the font, line breaks, and word spacing are the best possible choice. We work with family teams so each prompt has been play-tested in a real dynamic between loved ones. When you receive this deck, know that it is a token of love from many other families from your beloved culture. We believe we have some of the best, most natural translations in the world. Feel free to preview any of our games in their entirety before purchasing by&nbsp; downloading one of our digital decks . Do you have proof that this deck changes relationships? We did an impact study with 210 verified customers who used Parents Are Human with their loved ones. They reported these results among other findings: 98.90%&nbsp; of them agree that playing Parents Are Human helped them discover something new about their parent(s). 98.41% &nbsp;of them agree that they immediately felt closer to their parent(s) after playing Parents Are Human. 97.35%&nbsp; of them agree that Parents Are Human made them more open and understanding towards their parent(s). Will there be more languages in the future? Yes!! We absolutely can't wait to make our game into more languages! We have over 4,000+ requests at the moment and are prioritizing translations based on whichever ones gets the most requests. Please vote for your language here and we'll notify you as soon as we start. What if I decide it's not for me? Our Happiness Guarantee is simple: we offer free returns on all products purchased on this website within 100 days and a 100% refund, no questions asked. If you have a problem with your order (shipping mishaps, damaged/incorrect products, etc.), we will solve it, whatever it takes. Just reach out. Thank you for your trust and support. Rediscover Your Family Have heartfelt conversations you’ll remember forever with Parents Are Human . Grow Your Relationship Sometimes we are so busy growing up we forget our parents are growing old.&nbsp; We created a tool to get closer to our loved ones while we still can. It opens up even the most reserved dads . ""I found out what my dad favorite food was growing up. That dude is the hardest layers to peel so the fact that I got something out of him that’s amazing."" Kadin Tran Verified Customer It gets moms to share stories they've never told. ""My mom told me things she never told another soul. Maybe my parents are more open than most but they were pretty vulnerable even in their responses to the “light” questions."" Grace Lin Verified Customer Learn more about your grandparents that you ever have. ""I would say I'm pretty close with my parents, and speak their language fluently, but I loved how the cards delved deeper into their past. I learned a lot more about my grandparents than I ever have!"" Zayda Ortiz Verified Customer Document life stories for future generations. ""We’ve been playing this game as a family with my father in law who has dementia. We are logging his responses so that we can share them in the future. Great way to connect! Love this game."" Kim Qua Verified Customer We Transform Relationships Hear it from a few of our 100,000+ happy customers! life changer I literally use these cards every morning with my parents. I randomly select a (blue card) and text it to them. It’s helped our relationship so much. A couple of their responses brought tears to my eyes. As a bestselling author, trainer, and educator, I believe every family could benefit from this product. Thank you. Shay Sun Verified Customer An Opportunity for Healing I cannot thank you enough for the creation of these cards. I have only played a handful of these cards with my parents and in that short amount of time, I can already feel our relationship not only deepen but also heal -- and that is HUGE. Thank you for creating this vehicle to help us learn the stories of our parents. Nadine Palacio Verified Customer Learned Things I Never Would Have Otherwise I think every family should play this game together to find out more about our differences in the way we see life and to find a common ground where we can learn things we would have never learned without asking the questions on these cards. I learned things I never expected and I am so thankful. Can’t wait to play it more often with my family. Jamie Ha Verified Customer Wonderful idea Just played this last night. A family member was a bit nervous going into it, but I think it opened up. We recorded it, as it'll be a permanent record of some of our family's history. Even though our family can understand English, having Chinese on the reverse helped remove the dependence on the native English speakers on translating. Timothy Chu Verified Customer INCREDIBLE This is THE PERFECT game to bring home to the holidays. More than ever these last few years have taught us that life is short, life is precious - take the time now to get to know your parents & grandparents better. Kaye Rockwell Verified Customer A gift for deepening connections with loved ones I love the questions, that the decks are bilingual, and how my dad immediately opened up to the first thought-provoking question. I'm telling everyone I know about these decks (even if they don't need the second language!). I bought more than I needed to give them out as gifts. Thank you for creating this thoughtful product/game! Katharin Bettendorf Verified Customer love love love love this Once we opened the package, we couldn't stop opening it afterward to keep asking the questions. What a great idea even for friends, not only between parents and children. Well done. The elders are certainly smiling down on you. Now? How do I order 10 more sets? LOL And I'm being totally serious! Marvin Webb Verified Customer Great conversation starters My parents are immigrant Chinese and I've used these cards with them as well as other ethnic parents in my clinical practice as a I'm an Asian-American psychotherapist specializing in cultural issues. I'm so glad I found these as they are now an indispensable tool for engagement. Sam Louie Verified Customer Great way to connect with our older generation I loved how easy and thought provoking questions. Our elders may not want to answer then initially, but they will open up, eventually! I’ve grown closer to my grandma by asking her questions about her childhood. Theresa Le Verified Customer Wonderful This is such a wonderful project. The questions are so thoughtful. I've started asking my parents, aunts, and uncles. I've learned so much with some surprising answers. Two of my uncles felt honored that I was asking them and wanted to learn more about their lives. Thanks so much for creating this wonderful resource! Christina Dea Verified Customer Deep Conversations Immediately I played with some friends and immediately began learning more about them -- their families, preferences, personalities. This game has so much potential to teach empathy for parents of older generations, and friends alike. Harmony Zhang Verified Customer This really warms my heart The customer service is truly above-and-beyond and the product is really once of a kind. I applaud Joseph for this exceptional idea on how to connect with parents. He truly understand how difficult language barrier so if you’re reading this, Joseph– Thank you. Really. Nadia Chao Verified Customer Love this game! This is a great game that I tried to play with my hyperactive late 70s aged parents. I learned quite a bit from them that I felt were more connected since it was in Tagalog. Highly recommended if you’re one who has trouble breaking the ice with your folks. Junior Tidal Verified Customer Great way to combat Asian awkwardness The game really helped me understand my mom a bit more and put things into perspective for us. So much gets lost in translation, but her being able to read the question in mother tongue and respond accordingly helped significantly. Nhuy Vo Verified Customer One of the best games ever created! Thank you for creating such a priceless gift! I’ve already played w/my parents and I can honestly say, we’ve learned so much about each other & it’s brought us closer! Can’t wait to play through the entire deck! We can’t thank you enough!!! April Valeros Verified Customer AS SEEN ON My Parents Hand Pack Every Order With ♥️ I used our flagship deck to connect with my parents once a week for a year, and we went from barely ever talking for more than a decade to now working every day together. We're living proof that our decks work. When you order from us, Mama & Papa Lam will hand-pack then ship your order with the utmost love & care within a few hours. Sending you all our love. 🫶 Sign Up For Our Newsletter 💌 🔔 We'll share lessons on connecting more deeply with the people in your life, and let you know when we’re doing something special, launching new products, & more. ❤️ No spam, only hope, warmth, & love. Opt-out any time. I. PRODUCTS 🛒 All Products 🎁 Bundle & Save 📱 Digital Decks 📦 Wholesale ⭐️ Read Reviews ✍️ Leave a Review 🫶 In-Kind Donations II. LEARN About Us FAQs Blog Origins Request a Product Request a Language Help Us Translate III. CARE Accessibility Shipping Policy Refund Policy Privacy Policy UGC Policy Terms of Service Do Not Sell My Info IV. CONNECT Instagram Facebook TikTok X YouTube Careers Contact Us Thank you Mom & Dad, for every