eel like you're being forced to put your ethics on the line to close the sale. We achieve this by working WITH human behavior instead of against it... which eliminates all traces of sales pressure from your sales conversations and puts the control back in your hands. And as a result...this free's you up to focus on listening and connecting with your prospects, close more deals, and improve all aspects of your life as a result - this is NEPQ and it is the new model of selling. How is this different than all the other sales training out there? NEPQ leverages specific types of questions that taps into the highest form of communication and persuasion to work WITH human psychology instead of against it. While all other sales professionals are focused on using 100 year old methods, resorting to presentations and pitches... or worse... still focusing on the consultative form of selling... With NEPQ you'll cut the climb time of your sales career in half and hit the top of the leaderboard in record time. How long will it take to get my book? Your order will be processed immediately upon order. Shipping may take 5-7 business days depending on your state. If your order is international it may take 7-14 business days. Is there a guarantee? First, if you're looking for an out already... then this might not be the best product for you. We're looking for dedicated sales professionals who are looking to level up in their craft. With that being said... I already know that anyone who implements what they get in the Black Book of Questions ends up getting hooked and fast. Which is why my team and I put together the ""Money Where Your Mouth Is"" 30 Day Money Back Guarantee. If you grab the book, you go through the bonuses, and try it out and for whatever reason you feel like it didn't help you at all... Just email my support team and we'll refund every penny... and let you keep the Black Book of Questions as our way of saying thank you for betting on yourself and giving it a shot. SECU