https://www.authenticgame.com/pimp-your-lingo-offer-page,Course,Build flirting skills,,,"""Attracting Women Is Easy When You Know How To Talk To Them"", Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men, MORE REASONS TO GET STARTED TODAY, How a stammering shy guy discovered the secret to naturally attracting women in conversation..., Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Ben's Story&nbsp;, You'll Be Talking To Women Like A ""Natural"". Here's Why:, Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Johnny's Story&nbsp;, Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback:&nbsp;Aubrey's Story&nbsp;, Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Phillip's Story&nbsp;, It's Super Simple To Learn & Try Out In Your Everyday Life!, Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men, Pimp Your Lingo 2.0...What's Included And How Do You Get Access?, Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men, Let's Make This Risk Free For You!, 60 DAY RISK FREE 100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEE:&nbsp;, Ready? Then Here's How To Get Started!, Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men, PYL 2.0 FAQ, Almost There","pimp your lingo sales page ""Attracting Women Is Easy When You Know How To Talk To Them"" Watch this video to discover how to turn into a ""natural"" with women! &nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men Learn the art of attracting women in conversation. Get the new and upgraded Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 Program here! YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS! MORE REASONS TO GET STARTED TODAY How a stammering shy guy discovered the secret to naturally attracting women in conversation... &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; My name is Stephan Erdman. That's me in the picture right there and I am the creator of the Pimp Your Lingo System. It's for men who want to attract women in conversation without the need for silly pick up lines, scripts or sleazy routines! &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; This might be hard to believe but&nbsp;I came into my 20's&nbsp;with zero game, authentic or other. I wouldn't start a conversation with a girl even if she sent me 17 signs. And if she did talk to me first I&nbsp;would get uncomfortable, dry up and just go silent. Had real self esteem issues. Just didn't think I knew what to say. Let alone say something that would get her attracted in some way. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Then I&nbsp;tried the usual ""seduction pick up"" stuff. &nbsp;I am sure you have too, right? Sometimes it worked. Mostly it didn't. At least I tried something. But I felt like an actor...like a performing monkey. It didn't feel like power. It felt like neediness dressed up as ""skill"". So I had to dig deeper. I had to find a way to attract women and talk to women without the usual lines, performance based routines and all that crap. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; That's when I got lucky.&nbsp;I literally stumbled upon some of the secrets that have changed my life... like ""keyword backtracking"",&nbsp;principles to create instant rapport through words alone,&nbsp;blissfully natural ways to turn ANY conversation flirtatious and having fun in the process. I started to get predictable results and boom...this whole ""talking to women"" thing turned into actual fun! &nbsp; &nbsp; Turns out I had learned things most guys never learn about - so&nbsp;I started helping others. &nbsp;Now I've helped 1000's of men to overcome their shyness around women, attract women or go from zero dates to attracting a great girlfriend into their life. My videos have been viewed over 25 Million&nbsp;times. Organically. Pretty weird for a former shy guy from Germany.&nbsp;Ok. So that's me. But what does this mean for you?&nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Ben's Story&nbsp; &nbsp; You'll Be Talking To Women Like A ""Natural"". Here's Why: &nbsp; With the Pimp Your Lingo System you DON'T get&nbsp;sleazy tricks and weird pick up routines. &nbsp;If you've ever tried to use conventional pick up stuff you know how difficult that is to pull off without things getting weird. You feel fake and women can sense it. No words to learn here. The PYL system is easy to use and women just feel you're a guy that gets it. Anyone can use the PYL principles to attract women. Shy guys, confident guys, old guys young guys, no matter where you are in the world. Because it's flexible and subtle, you can adjust your approach with these flexible methods depending on your surroundings and your personality. It's easy to practice even if you're a busy professional. &nbsp;You can&nbsp;take most of the simpler methods&nbsp;and use it for your interactions during your day. Try it, play with it, notice the changes. When you can do it without thinking, move on to the next one. Simple. (More about that below) It's so subtle the girls on the program didn't notice what I was doing even after I told them. :-) So you'll never have to worry about coming across as creepy or anything like that. This program makes you stand out in the right way.&nbsp; Even if you think you don't have an interesting personality, this program basically gives you one, even just by giving you the understanding and tools to have an amazing time when you talk to women The principles work for you in face to face interactions with women, phone conversations and of course, texting. Every stage of the seduction process,&nbsp;you've got an unfair advantage over all the other guys. The PYL fundamentals won't just help you attract women, they'll also help you be confident and persuasive in ANY social interaction, at work or in the club. Life changing. Let's keep it real. I can't ""guarantee"" you my results or those of my students. Everybody is different. Your level of success depends on how you understand, practise and use the techniques. But the ideas I have condensed into this program have transformed me from a shy and awkward guy into a confident man. I am now at ease opening my mouth with complete strangers and love to engage, meet and connect and flirt with attractive women and I've dated some incredible women over the years.&nbsp;The methods could do the same for you. Ok. Now before you get this check out some more real life feedback from guys who have used the program before you: &nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Johnny's Story&nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback:&nbsp;Aubrey's Story&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo Customer Feedback: Phillip's Story&nbsp; It's Super Simple To Learn & Try Out In Your Everyday Life! &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Just like these clients above this program could enable you to get in control when you're talking to women maybe for the first time in your life. It could also make you more attractive to women when you talk to them and on dates without them even noticing why. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; When you listen to this program on your mp3 player, smartphone or computer you will hear me demonstrating different techniques. Techniques that help you create rapport, to connect, to flirt and seduce a girl through conversation. &nbsp;You also hear the reactions from the girls. All you need to do is follow along and start practising the techniques in your own day to day life.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; How much time do you need? Just spend about 10 minutes a day listening to one of the tracks once or twice. Then experiment with the technique during your day. Once you're able to use it and you've noticed the response you get...move on to the next one. Simple. Easy. Fast. ;-) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Within a few weeks you find yourself meeting women and having conversations with them. You will have more options when you talk to women. And do things right and almost without thinking. You will have fun in conversations with women.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Ok...so now you know what Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 can do for you, let's do a quick recap: Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS! Pimp Your Lingo 2.0...What's Included And How Do You Get Access? Here's a summary of everything you get as part of the Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men Program Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - The Art Of Verbal Foreplay &nbsp;| PART 1: INNER GAME | PART 2: CONNECTION FACTORS | PART 3: ATTRACTION FACTORS | NEW: PART 4: ADVANCED ATTRACTION FACTORS | NEW: PART 5: CONVERSATION FUN TACTICS This New And Updated Advanced Conversation Skills For Men is an audio program.&nbsp; The equivalent of 8 CD's chokeful of pure ""love life changing"" content.&nbsp; (21 Brand New Tracks Added)&nbsp; It's delivered in mp3 format so it's easily downloadable to your itunes and mp3 player. &nbsp;It will cost you only $99.00 from this special page. (normally $147.00) 4 HIGHLY RELEVANT + VALUABLE FREE BONUS TRAININGS: &nbsp; Using Pimp Your Lingo Online Video Training (Value $27.00) Pimp Your Lingo Special Report (16 page pdf -advanced pyl strategies explained - Value $27.00) Instant Rapport Approach Formula Video Training (Value $27.00) NEW BONUS TRAINING ADDED: 6 Ways To Develop A Voice That Attracts Women (with Ivana Basic - Value $47.00)&nbsp; After you order the program you get 2 emails from me:&nbsp; One email with access details to the private members area where you can download the program and get further surprise bonuses. The other asking you to confirm your subscription to the vip members updates which means you will get relevant advice, articles and add ons.&nbsp;&nbsp; Remember: The program is&nbsp;designed to be listened to when it's convenient regularly and repeatedly&nbsp;so that the methods and concepts become a part of your tools as effortlessly as possible. Lastly: It's important to USE my program.&nbsp;If you don't talk to anyone after purchasing the product it will probably make you feel good but it is a set of powerful tools you must USE. Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS! Let's Make This Risk Free For You! 60 DAY RISK FREE 100% SATISFACTION GUARANTEE:&nbsp; You've got a whole 60 days to try the program! If&nbsp;for ANY reason&nbsp;the program doesn't work for you simply send me an email within 60 days to&nbsp; [email&#160;protected] &nbsp;and let me know and I'll refund you and thank you for trying it out! Ready? Then Here's How To Get Started! Here's all you need to do to have this program in your media player/itunes in a couple of minutes: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;1. Click the ""YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS!"" button below! &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2. Go through the simple, secure paypal/stripe checkout (pay by credit card or paypal) &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3. Return to our site when prompted (on paypal) and make sure you sign in for member updates &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4. We send you an automated email with log in instructions for the members area &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 5. Go, log in and download the program and get started right now!&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Look. I won't pretend that this site is going to explode in 3 seconds to make you buy my program right now like most of these fake sales pages for the latest hype ebook. The truth is it's still going to be here tomorrow, probably. But you're sitting here and you're reading this and you know you want to attract women so you know this is a good fit for you. That's why I know when you order today you'll be glad you did! &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; One more thing. Ask yourself this: Are you willing to spend 1 more day feeling out of control when it comes to talking to women? Because now you know it doesn't have to be that way. And you know that life moves forward, whether you learn this or not. And your life only changes when you do something different. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; This stuff is essential for any man. If you can't make people LIKE you and women LOVE you when you talk to them it costs you in all aspects of your life. Harsh but true. &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;If you still have questions about the program please email me at [email&#160;protected] . Or else...go ahead and click the ""YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS"" button below and get started today! &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Ready to change your (love) life? &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Then join us inside,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Stephan&nbsp; Pimp Your Lingo 2.0 - Advanced Conversation Skills For Men Get ready to attract the girl of your dreams in conversation. Easily practise the techniques in your day to day life! YES, GIVE ME INSTANT ACCESS! PYL 2.0 FAQ Frequently Asked Questions About The Program Question: I am a busy professional. I don't have time to go out for hours to talk to women. Will this be helping me? Answer: Perfect. Sure, you need some time for a social life...but the best thing about the PYL 2.0 Program is that you can practise most of the methods in your everyday life. I've made it very easy to implement. Question: I am not in the US or UK. Will this program work for me in my country? Answer: Yes, the Pimp Your Lingo conversation system is flexible and can be adapted to your culture and society. A large percentage of our customers are from outside the US and the UK. We have incredible feedback from men all over the world who have applied this system with great results. Question: Can I get a refund if I don't like it? Answer: Yes, you can get a refund for 60 days by emailing me. But of course, my first goal is to help you achieve your goals. So you could also email me first and ask me for a little extra help if there's a specific sticking point you're struggling with. Question: I speak a different language in my country. Will this program really help me? Answer: Yes. If you can understand English to listen to the tracks you can apply the principles and ideas in your own language without a problem. This program isn't about lines or routines so the PYL system works in all languages to the best of my knowledge. You’ll just need to apply it in your language. Question: How do I access the program? Answer: After purchasing, you'll get an email with login and password information. If you have purchased other programs of mine your login and password usually stays the same and you'll