a table. First, here's the context of my company: ### company ### YOUR COMPANY'S INFO ### company ### Follow these steps: Basic Pitch Deck Structure: Create the first row of the table and list all the relevant sections of the pitch deck: Intro, Status Quo, Product, Market, Why Us, and The Ask. Company Stage: In the second row, describe the current stage of the company under each section heading. Highlight key milestones, development stages, and readiness for market entry. The Intro Section: Elaborate on how to craft a compelling introduction that hooks the audience’s attention, explaining the company’s mission and vision succinctly. The Status Quo Section: Discuss the current market situation that the startup is addressing. Emphasize the pain points with current solutions that the startup aims to overcome. The Product Section: Describe the product or service in detail. Include its unique features that differentiate it from competitors. The Market Section: Provide a detailed analysis of the market size, growth potential, customer demographics, and how the startup positions itself within this market. The Why Us Section: Explain why the startup is uniquely positioned to succeed. Highlight the team's expertise, strategic partnerships, and early achievements. The Ask: Clearly state what the startup is seeking from investors. Visual Enhancement: Recommend types of visuals to include. Review and Refinement: Provide guidelines on how to refine the content for each section. Remember, you are the one crafting the table by filling it up. If I didn't share enough information, be creative. Take a deep breath and work on this problem step-by-step. ____ The free version of Gamma is already so good. But if you need more, I have discount codes left. ↳ I partnered with them to get the 1st month at $1. ♻️ Repost this video if you learned something. …more 1,034 490 Comments Like Comment Share Copy LinkedIn Facebook X Ruben Hassid Master AI before it masters you. 9mo Report this comment