ars. I am from South Africa and I just moved to LA. Been doing the course for 8 Months now, what a miracle!!!!!!!!!! And it has helped to let my instrument be what it is supposed to be. [Per is] like the BRUCE LEE of the VOICE!…. Sean Van Blerk ""In 20 Years I've Never Had A Teacher Approach Singing Like Per Does"" Oh my goodness, I am so beyond grateful for this program. I literally only started yesterday and it's already rocker my world. I had a 4 hour jazz gig last night and had more freedom in my scatting and endurance through the gig. I've studied voice for almost 20 years but have never had a teacher approach singing like Per does. THANK YOU! Lola Kristine Hennike YES, I WANT ACCESS TO THIS SESSION! ""It Has Helped Get The Best Out Of My Voice!"" The Sing With Freedom program is fantastic! I would highly recommend them to anyone who wants to improve their singing. Per's approach is unique and it has really helped me to relax and get the best out of my voice! Cathy Vard Triple Platinum Selling Artist with Vard Sisters - Ireland ""Already Singing With Freedom! It's Amazing!"" I work fulltime as a freelance vocalist in Australia, and I realised that even though I could sing well, there were still many areas that I needed to develop. For the record, I have spent $$$ on singing lessons &amp; other courses and I must admit, when I stumbled…… Evelyn Duprai ""To Deliver Consistent Performances Night After Night"" After singing professionally with a rock band as well as a solo performer for 20 plus years… I always found it challenging to try and keep some kind of consistency in my night to night performance. Well over the years some of the bad nights led to vocal polyps and nodules….. Remy Lambert Hello I’m Per Bristow Allow me to provide you with this opportunity to experience something absolutely remarkable about your voice. Singing is such an amazing activity, whether we're entertaining a sold-out stadium, or creating music with friends, or having fun by ourselves. And what's even more remarkable is that we can indeed dramatically improve our voice. And when we do, singing of course becomes even more enjoyable. But How Can We Improve Effectively? Well, what if there's a way that has proven exceptionally effective, but it's not about singing scales or learning ""breath support""? Would it be a bad idea to find out what it's all about? 😉 Well, that's why I'm providing you with this session. The Powerful Process That Releases Hidden Tension/Restrictions I'm immensely grateful that singers of all level and styles have benefited from my method for the last 16 years. But realize that the incredible improvements they experience are not because of me. They improve because of the new kinesthetic awareness and muscle isolation skills that they develop. Let's Say, For Example, You'd Like To Be Able To: Release hidden tension&nbsp; that is currently holding back your voice but that you may not even be aware of! Sing with more power but with less effort! Sing high notes&nbsp; with less effort and more choices&nbsp; Get a richer and more resonant voice Gain &nbsp;greater endurance – to be able to &nbsp;s ing for a long time without getting tired, and recover quicker (a vital skill of any performer.) Eliminate that break in your voice and sing with a seemless voice! (You’ll see the live demonstration how and why the voice cracks/“breaks” and why it doesn’t have to, so you can sing your favorite songs with greater joy and ease.) Extend phrases and sing longer notes! (You’ll see why it has little to do with your breathing - a shocking discovery for many.) Sing more accurately on key! (You’ll discover why this has less to do with your ear than most people think - which also is many times shocking for people.) Experience greater confidence and FREEDOM when you sing! And much, much more! You'll Learn How We Do This, And Why It's Vital To Let Go Of Singing Scales.&nbsp; You’ll also realize why common statements such as “feel as if you’re yawning”, “use breath-support ”, "" sing through your mask” , “sing from your stomach” , etc. become detrimental for so many. Ultimately, you are going to discover how this process of setting your voice free becomes so rewarding to not only effectively develop your physical instrument, but also to set YOU free! Register Here &gt;&gt; Per Bristow’ s mind/body/spirit approach to effectively train the human voice has evolved out of his background as a child prodigy violin player, elite youth athlete, lead singer in the biggest box office successes in Swedish theatre history, in addition to his deep knowledge in anatomy, peak performance psychology, voice, sports physiology and more. Upon moving to Los Angeles, he quickly became known as the go-to coach for numerous singers and speakers, and his home study training has for the last 16 years helped people in 146 countries. His live events have sold out in 15 countries on 4 continents. Enter your first name and your email address, and the email with the link to the session will automatically be sent to you YES! SEND ME THE VIDEO A Few Voices From Social Media: GET THE SESSION HERE &gt;&gt; © Per Bristow contact Privacy Terms and Condition"
