PM EST Perfect for Agencies, Founders, and SEO Pros. Freelancers looking to dive deep into how SEO can get their clients results. Entrepreneurs who need SEO content that actually ranks—and sells. Agencies that want to scale content production without sacrificing quality. Reserve My Spot for $27 What You’ll Walk Away With: A fully-optimized website ready to climb the Google Rankings Secure Your Spot High quality content built &amp; published built with the help of AI Secure Your Spot Authority building backlinks secured to boost performance Secure Your Spot Your technical issues fixed, automatically. Saving you time and money Secure Your Spot Your Search Atlas dashboard set up for long-term success Secure Your Spot They Took the Challenge Now They’re Ranking on Page 1 Why Most SEO Training Fails And What We’re Doing Instead Most courses drown you in theory. Most “gurus” make it more complicated than it needs to be. This challenge is different. It’s hands-on, Search Atlas-powered, and focused on execution. Secure Your Spot Event Schedule Five Days of Unmissable Value Get daily sessions packed with practical tips, tested systems, and real results. So you walk away smarter, faster, and more search-ready than ever. DAY 1 Aug 18 Setup, Holistic SEO, &amp; Technical Fixes with OTTO Learn the core pillars of Holistic SEO and how to fix the major technical factors that hold your rankings back. DAY 2 Aug 19 Create Content that Ranks at Scale In this session, we&#8217;ll show you what it takes to create content that ranks and the steps you need to take to build high quality content, fast. DAY 3 Aug 20 How to Build Authority in 2025 How we teach you to build authority gets you ranked on Google &amp; in the LLMs. We even cover the costs to build back links and produce press releases to make sure you get an easy win. DAY 4 Aug 21 Optimizing for Local Businesses During this session, we&#8217;ll cover the strategies to getting your clients ranked, what really matters to Google, and how to automate manual tasks. DAY 5 Aug 22 UX Signals &amp; Google Ads This session covers two critical areas of search: the UX signals Google listens for and how to win with Google Ads. Start Winning Now Key Topics What You’ll Learn Designed for marketers and SEO teams ready to rank, this challenge breaks down the exact strategies, workflows, and tools used to grow traffic—fast and sustainably. Ranking with strategy How top marketers use data-backed plans (not guesswork) to climb SERPs with purpose. SEO and content, in alignment How to sync your keyword targeting, content briefs, and optimization for compounding growth. Executing fast without breaking things How to ship optimized pages quickly—without sacrificing quality, clarity, or performance. Start Winning Now In 5 days, you won't just ""learn about SEO""... You’ll DO the SEO that gets you ranked Let Me In Challenge Starts Monday, August 18 AT 1pm EST Here’s How the Challenge Works Join the Challenge Sign up today to lock in your spot. Join Daily Live Trainings Learn + implement bite-sized wins each day. Complete Your SEO Sprint Get your site ranking-ready in 5 days. Daily Calls 8/18 – 8/22 at 1pm EST Everything You Get When You Join Included Item Value Daily SEO Training Sessions $2997 Access to Private Slack Community $297 SEO Sprint Worksheets + Checklists $97 VIP Upgrade (Recordings &amp; Bonuses) Optional Total Value $3391 Yours Today for Just $27 Join the Challenge Now Meet Your SEO Coach: Manick Bhan Manick Bhan is one of the most respected SEO engineers in the world. As the CEO and CTO of Search Atlas, he’s personally ranked thousands of websites on Page 1 of Google; from Fortune 500 companies to startups to personal brands. He’s been featured in USA Today, Yahoo Finance, and Search Engine Journal, and is trusted by some of the fastest-growing companies in the world to engineer their SEO success. In this Challenge, Manick will personally guide you step-by-step, using the same strategies that power some of the internet’s top-ranking sites and now, your site can be next. Secure Your Spot Secure Your Spot Meet Your SEO Coach: Arman Advani Arman Advani is a seasoned digital marketing executive with a track record of driving organic growth for some of today’s most competitive brands. As Partner and Director of Search at Search Atlas, where he helps shape product innovation and strategy. His deep expertise in technical SEO, content strategy, and analytics has been key to making Search Atlas one of the most powerful platforms for executing high-impact SEO at scale. In this Challenge, Arman will be your guide through the Search Atlas platform, showing you exactly how to apply the SEO concepts Manick teaches using the tools top marketers rely on to win in search. We Start August 18th! Save Your Seat Before It’s Too Late. Days Hours Minutes Seconds Spots are limited to ensure every participant gets the personalized support they need. Reserve My Spot for $27 Frequently Asked Questions What if I can't attend live? This is a LIVE active workshop, you get the best results by attending each daily session. If you’re unable to join, our VIP members (VIP costs an additional $97) will get the challenge call recordings each day. However, if you can’t commit the time to attend the trainings and do the daily tasks, you will not benefit from the challenge. How long are the daily sessions? Sessions will run for 60-90 minutes for all challenge participants. If you’re a VIP, you’ll be able to stick around longer to get your individual questions answered. Is this challenge beginner-friendly? Absolutely! This challenge is designed for SEOs of all skill levels. It’s designed to give you the step-by-step instructions you need to climb up Google’s rankings from one of the world’s leading experts. What if I’m already doing SEO — will I still benefit? Yes! SEO is always changing and this challenge is the culmination of the latest research by Manick and the Search Atlas team. At best you’ll have a proven strategy that gets your site ranking and at worst it will be a very solid refresher. How does the Search Atlas trial work? All challenge members will be prompted to sign up for a 7-day trial of Search Atlas to work along with Manick during the challenge. Our VIP members are given an extended 30-day trial to keep the momentum going. What’s your refund policy? If you decide the Challenge isn’t right for you within 48 hours of the first Challenge session starting, just let us know, and we’ll process a refund. © All copyrights reserved, Search Atlas 2025 Terms of Use Privacy Policy Data Privacy Agreement Refund Policy Terms of Use Privacy Policy Data Privacy Agreement Refund Policy"
