A Proven Process for Startup Founders by Martin Bell, Trusted by 25,000+ Startups",100 Tasks Checklist,,"The Ultimate Founders Checklist to Systematically Launch &amp; Scale Your Startup 3-5x Faster in 2025 🚀, #1 Battle-Tested Process for Startup Founders in 2025 🚀, Building Startups Is Not Magic. It&#x27;s Cause &amp; Effect., Stage 1: Bulletproof Setup, Stage 2: Fast Launch, Stage 3: Systematic Scale, Ready to Supercharge Your Startup? 🚀, #1 Battle-Tested Process for Startup Founders in 2025 🚀, Our Startup Building Story, Westerwelle Foundation, The Factory, University of Amsterdam, Got Questions? We&#x27;ve Got You Covered., Start your free trial, Ready to Supercharge Your Startup? 🚀","100 Tasks Checklist Log in Buy for $7 (Usually $199) Buy for $7 Free 1.5 Hour Video Training The Ultimate Founders Checklist to Systematically Launch &amp; Scale Your Startup 3-5x Faster in 2025 🚀 A Proven Process for Startup Founders by Martin Bell, Trusted by 25,000+ Startups Start for $1 Watch Demo Talk to sales Talk to sales 25,000+ Startups Trust Us #1 Battle-Tested Process for Startup Founders in 2025 🚀 100 Tasks Checklist &amp; Overview Poster Structured approach that really simplifies all the ins and outs of building a startup Proven 3 Phase Process 25,000+ Companies The same proven startup building process that launched the likes of Zalando, Delivery Hero, and more Bonus: 1.5 Hour Video Training How to launch your startup 3-5x faster Bonus: 18 Powersheets Plug-&amp;-play startup building toolkit Bonus: Startup AI &amp; PM Tool 1 Month for free, easily cancel at anytime - no questions asked 4.7 from 500+ reviews 95% OFF Sale Ends on Thursday, April 10th Checklist $7 $199 Lifetime Access $7 $199 Lifetime Checklist Access Day 1 to IPO 100 Tasks all functions Building Startups Is Not Magic. It&#x27;s Cause &amp; Effect. Martin Bell takes you through the three stages of building a successful startup. It encompasses all the functions of the value-chain including ideation, fundraising, developing your MVP, rapid scaling, and more. 1 Week 1-6 Stage 1: Bulletproof Setup Build the unshakeable foundation and bulletproof your strategy that will power your startup to success. Start With Problems Identify and validate a problem worth solving that has real market demand. Plan Mission Define your startup&#x27;s mission, vision, and strategic roadmap. Assemble Core Team Recruit the right co-founders and early team members with complementary skills. Collect Ideas Systematically generate, evaluate, and prioritize innovative solutions. Determine Business Models Create a sustainable business model centered around your validated problem. 2 week 7-13 Stage 2: Fast Launch Transform your vision into reality by quickly building, funding, and launching your market-ready product. Develop MVP Rapidly build and test your minimum viable product to prove market fit. Raise Capital + Fundraising Toolkit Secure pre-seed funding to fuel your startup&#x27;s initial growth. Build Functions Establish core operational functions across all business areas. Setup KPI Reports Implement data tracking and reporting systems to measure success. Go Live Create massive hype around your product with a big launch. 3 Week 14-20 Stage 3: Systematic Scale Accelerate into exponential growth and establish your venture as an industry-leading powerhouse. Raise Growth Capital Raise additional funding rounds to accelerate growth. Build Culture Build a strong company culture that attracts and retains top talent. Learn from Data Use data insights to drive all strategic decisions and operations. Optimize Functions + Powersheets Continuously improve and streamline all business functions. Best-Practice Company Achieve sustainable, exponential growth as a best-practice venture. &quot; The 100 Tasks is a true necessity for any entrepreneur! The playbook is full of useful insights and the Slack community helps people support one another. I wish we had this systematic approach when we were building WeTransfer.&quot; -Nalden Co-Founder, We-Transfer &quot;Most venture studios possess — at most! — 50% of the know-how contained in the Playbook. Due to the gigantic value packed into this startup manual , I told Martin that he can basically charge whatever he wants for the System.&quot; -Michael van Lier CEO, We Are Builders &quot;Martin&#x27;s process was an easy-to-follow instruction manual that explained many tasks that weren&#x27;t even on our radar.&quot; -Dominik Ziems Lead of KPMG Project KOSMOS &quot;The 100 Tasks got us to MVP at lightning speed and helped us clinch great investors ! I&#x27;m also using the 100 Tasks to start two new projects. And I&#x27;ve been given a board position at another company. Thanks, Martin!&quot; Jonathan Fried Founder, in-Court app Ready to Supercharge Your Startup? 🚀 Apply the same proven startup building process that launched the likes of Zalando, Delivery Hero and 25,000+ startups to your company. #1 Battle-Tested Process for Startup Founders in 2025 🚀 100 Tasks Checklist &amp; Overview Poster Structured approach that really simplifies all the ins and outs of building a startup Proven 3 Phase Process 25,000+ Companies The same proven startup building process that launched the likes of Zalando, Delivery Hero, and more Bonus: 1.5 Hour Video Training How to launch your startup 3-5x faster Bonus: 18 Powersheets Plug-&amp;-play startup building toolkit Bonus: Startup AI &amp; PM Tool 1 Month for free, easily cancel at anytime - no questions asked 4.7 from 500+ reviews 95% OFF Sale Ends on Thursday, April 10th Checklist $7 $199 Lifetime Access $7 $199 Lifetime Checklist Access Our Startup Building Story &quot; I found myself one day in what felt like a closed-off world: Knee-deep in the startup landscape and advising corporate launchpads. ‍ At some point, things became repetitive. Regardless of the industry, background, or intricacies of a company, the steps were always the same when it came to building. Afterwards, I started to think about how useful this could be to a lot of people. More than that, I started asking the question of why exactly this knowledge was shut away behind closed doors. ‍ I realized that there was a process behind it all and a clear pattern to building a venture. I distilled all of my venture building knowledge into one place and began to share it with the broader startup community. ‍ The 100 Tasks was built to expand the borders of this bubble I had found myself in some years ago. To empower whoever has an idea to turn that idea into something tangible. The 100 Tasks was built to democratize entrepreneurship. &quot; ‍ - Martin Bell, CEO &amp; Founder Watch the Ted Talk Westerwelle Foundation Helping build emerging markets throughout the African Continent! Our 100 Tasks Framework is being utilized by non-profit incubators to empower local entrepreneurs. The Factory Decreasing entrepreneurial risk for a bubbling tech scene! The 100 Tasks is helping foster the growth of two of Europe’s prime startup hubs in Berlin and Hamburg. University of Amsterdam Bridging the gap between the classroom and the market! Providing the 100 Tasks to the UvA incubator to bring a level of practicality not present in current academia. Got Questions? We&#x27;ve Got You Covered. Why is this so cheap? Not only do we believe in giving value up-front but we are also on a mission to democratise entrepreneurship. We also offer higher end products such as our flagship 100 Tasks System to fund our growth. Does this qualify as a business expense? For sure, once you purchase you will automatically be sent an invoice. You can business expense this purchase and if you are a registered business you can get your VAT refunded as well. Is this for me? If you want to launch and scale a startup – then yes. The 100 Task System is for founders, entrepreneurs, innovators, consultants, managers, corporations, and anyone who is involved in helping a new venture take off the ground (or has plans to do so). Does this work for my industry? The 100 Tasks was designed to be applicable regardless of the industry or geography of the venture. At Rocket Internet and Bell Ventures, Martin worked with B2C and B2B companies across all different types of industries and sectors. The 100 Tasks contain the strategies, best-practices, and specific tools that he used to make these ventures successful. The System will enable you to apply these strategies and to adapt them to your particular venture and industry. To name a few, Martin worked most recently with companies in spaces such as E-Mobility, HealthTech, FinTech, Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Blockchain, Internet-of-Things, e-Commerce, Food, and Logistics. Have another question? You can reach our support team at 100tasks@bell.ventures. Start your free trial Can’t find the answer you’re looking for? Please chat to our friendly team. Get in touch Ready to Supercharge Your Startup? 🚀 Apply the same proven startup building process that launched the likes of Zalando, Delivery Hero and 25,000+ startups to your company. Start Now for $7 (Usually $199)"
