nly 9 weeks, not only web development but also how to challenge yourself and grow as a person!"" Carolina Cota Backend Developer N26 ""I loved my experience at Le Wagon, especially the last 2 weeks of teamwork: Developing an idea, visualising it in mock-ups, breaking it down into development tasks, and pitching the final product. This is the essence of product culture!"" Adrien Moison Head of Product Back Market ""Le Wagon changed my life. I went from designing ads to building an app that eventually got Google’s attention. Now me and my co-founders (who I also met at Le Wagon) all work at Google living our best lives."" Allan Holmes Interaction Designer Google ""The bootcamp gave me the opportunity to learn about the full process of building a product and to confirm I particularly love the design and frontend side of things."" Caroline Bixner Senior Service Designer Deloitte Digital ""Only two months after finishing the Bootcamp, I landed my first job as a Junior Software Engineer. That would not have been possible without the amazing career support from Le Wagon’s staff."" Mathieu Longé Software Engineer 99designs ""I expected a lot from Le Wagon for my Data Science formation and the global experience was even better: the content of the formation and the custom learning platform were really well structured and all the people at Le Wagon very helpful."" Josselin Grouas Data/IA Manager Consultant Niji ""I warmly recommend Le Wagon to anyone who wants to sky rocket their career in our increasingly digital world. Le Wagon is more than just a coding school it’s a proper experience and a human melting pot."" Christophe Arendt Data Engineer Capgemini ""I am grateful for the valuable knowledge and experience that this program provided me with. I would encourage anyone who wants to change to a career in tech to join this excellent program."" Asma Laaribi Developer Shopify ""Le Wagon has a huge emphasis on culture and community. The energy is incredibly positive &amp; the Teachers/Teacher Assistants are always happy to help and answer questions."" Thomas Temple Software Engineer Hall &amp; Wilcox ""Le Wagon is a great way to get into tech and learn a new skill with good teachers to support your journey and definitely don’t be shy to ask 100 questions like I did."" Ștefania-Ella Centea Junior Product Manager ASDA ""After 3 years working in Investment Banking, I decided to update my skill-set with some tools that I could use for whatever my next professional challenge would be."" Ayelen Klas Sr. Growth &amp; Operations Manager Razor Group ""Le Wagon truly changed my life with coding. Coming from a sales background, it enabled me to acquire the technical knowledges to start a developer career."" Isabelle Ferrier Web Developer amlconsult GmbH ""“In a matter of weeks, I gained a high-level understanding of data engineering challenges and the technical capabilities needed to take on those opportunities. Since completing the course, I have been much more confident and efficient in my work.”"" Raphael Hidalgo Data Scientist Junior Finfrog ""An insane experience! The feeling of being really more comfortable technically, of being able to take part in many other projects. And above all, the feeling of truly being part of a passionate and caring community!"" Adeline Cortijos Growth Marketing Manager Aktio FAQ Your questions answered Join an interactive info session Explore our bootcamps in Web Development, Data Science &amp; AI, Data Analytics, Data Engineering and Growth Marketing bootcamps Get guidance&nbsp;from our Admissions Managers on application steps, important dates, and financing options. Learn more about the different flexible learning formats Ask questions about the bootcamp application process and your next career steps 4.98 / 5 5200+ reviews 4.98 / 5 2,927 reviews 4.98 / 5 2,698 reviews 4.9 / 5 1,279 reviews Loading form... Get a detailed look at our AI Software course Understand the goal of the bootcamp Find out more about the cours