ow are so new, unknown &amp; overwhelming. And at the heart of it all, you just want to make a great impact on the world., See, the world of online business is so different from just a few years ago. And all the challenges coaches are facing now are so new, unknown &amp; overwhelming., And at the heart of it all, you just want to make a great impact on the world., ...Back in 2017, I’d dropped out of high school to go all-in on my marketing agency., I was doing local business lead generation, but my real passion was growth., The universe must have known because a man showed up at my office &amp; asked me to help him sell his book., I said yes &amp; that one moment changed the course of my life &amp; everything I thought was possible in business., We launched his book &amp; it blew up- doing $30k a month from just the book funnel sales (which was a big deal for me at the time) - not counting backend premium offer buyers!, ...Back in 2017, I’d dropped out of high school to go all-in on my marketing agency. I was doing local business lead generation, but my real passion was growth., The universe must have known because a man showed up at my office &amp; asked me to help him sell his book., I said yes &amp; that one moment changed the course of my life &amp; everything I thought was possible in business., We launched his book &amp; it blew up- doing $30k a month from just the book funnel sales (which was a big deal for me at the time) - not counting backend premium offer buyers!, I had spent years studying the most successful coaches, entrepreneurs &amp; books in the world. ​ ​, And I noticed a pattern..., The most successful coaches, weren't the ones doing  ALL, THE THINGS., They weren't constantly, creating new offers, They definitely weren't spending, all their time chasing the next, client, They weren't grinding, themselves into the ground, chasing every new shiny object, The most successful coaches weren't, the ones doing ALLTHE THINGS., They weren't constantly crea