Apps WITHOUT Learning To Code",Webinar,A full-stack template for modern web applications.,Announcing A NEW Way To BuildApps WITHOUT Learning To Code,"Webinar Announcing A NEW Way To Build Apps WITHOUT Learning To Code Limited Space Available. 00 HOUR : 00 MINUTE : 00 SECOND Sebastian here. I never do this, but every once in a while you come across a great opportunity you need to share. 9 months ago I challenged myself to build an app with nothing but AI. No learning to code , no $10,000 developer fee , just me, my laptop and an ai chatbot. Last month, the co-pilot born from that challenge did $61,000 in annual subscriptions with a 1.3% refund rate . This works. This copilot became my ai coding superpower, helping me cut credit usage by 20–30% and hallucinations by &gt;60% . I built this copilot on purpose. You see, Lovable, Cursor, Base44 etc sell the dream of “build any app by chatting with AI.” The truth is these tools don&#x27;t ship real products. They gamify building. You get to taste what&#x27;s possible, but you never finish . That&#x27;s why your apps aren&#x27;t live. That&#x27;s why your last months Lovable bill was $500 . “But Sebastian, if thats true, how did you use these tools to build an app that made $61,000 !” - you&#x27;re right, it&#x27;d be a massive disservice to you if I teased this but never actually showed you the tactical steps I took. So, here&#x27;s the deal: I can&#x27;t show you here, but on this class I&#x27;ll reveal ALL my tactics . I won&#x27;t hold back or keep anything to myself. It&#x27;s not just me, you&#x27;ll also see how Juan use this approach to build a micro-startup in 4 weeks and get his first 100 users all from his college dorm, and Matt build a CRM while running a massive company. We&#x27;ve cracked a repeatable way to build without learning to code, cut credit usage by 20–30% and hallucinations by &gt;60% . If you&#x27;ve been waiting for the moment to become a founder with millions of users, or at the very least build an app with predictable monthly revenue - this is it. Register for the free training to unlock the tactics I used to build an app with AI and make $61,000 . ➜ Click Here To Register Disclaimer: Are these results typical? No. It takes a certain type of person to build and ship AI apps that generate $61,000. Several of my students build apps that do $1,000-$10,000 per month, but there are people who never finish their builds, make $0, and some who even lose money on AI credits. Which type of person are you? Come to this training event and find out."
