powerful energy for yourself and others, guiding clients into holistic harmony in the body. Certified in 4 Months. Become a Energy Activation Therapist in just four months and start applying your new skillset right away. --> --> Prestigious Accreditations. InnerCamp is accredited by The Complementary Medical Association, CPD certified, and a member of the International Breathwork Foundation. Science-backed applications. Learn from the leading edge of scientific discovery in the energy field. All-in-One Learning. Access holistic expertise, lifetime support, business guidance, and a global community—online or hybrid so you can stay connected wherever you are in the world. Proven Session Structure. Gain a step-by-step framework to apply immediately after graduation so your sessions are profound and effective from day one. Join a Global Community. Over 2,000 participants from 45+ countries have chosen InnerCamp since 2018. Book your spot --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> Alexis Alcalá, founder --> --> Alexis Alcalá, founder --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> --> ACCREDITED PROGRAMS InnerCamp is an accredited school InnerCamp is registered and accredited by the Complementary Medical Association. InnerCamp is a member school of the International Breathwork Foundation. Our courses are accredited by the leading independent CPD accreditation institution. Curriculum Facilitated by 300 hours Curriculum ENERGY WORK 150 hours Awaken and harness the powerful Kundalini activation energy within you and your clients Ancient Taoist energy techniques to balance and circulate energy throughout the body How to align and heal the body's energy centers (chakras) Tantric breathing techniques to connect with inner energy, awareness, and release tension Release physical and emotional blockages in your clients with tantric de-armouring massage Methods to cleanse and protect the auric energy field Develop and enhance intuitive abilities by learning to sense and work with subtle energy fields. Specialized tantric energy exercises that amplify and channel sexual and spiritual energy Advanced healing techniques that work at the quantum level Healing and energizing the womb or hara (the body's energy center) How to use crystals, pendulums, and tuning forks in your client sessions INTIMACY 20 hours Tantric polarity techniques to balance masculine and feminine energies Tantric intimacy and pleasure practices that enhance intimacy and pleasure The importance of intimacy and vulnerability in building trust and closeness in relationships The power of shadow work in your client sessions Tools to establish clear boundaries and consent practices The art of sacred touch techniques How to exchange and balance energy during intimate moments TRAUMA RELEASE 50 hours Effective emotional release methods to unlock stored emotions Therapeutic movement to reconnect with the body, release tension, and promote emotional well-being Body-based approaches to trauma healing with somatic experiencing techniques The energetic impact of trauma on the body The connection between the body and mind in trauma recovery for yourself and your clients Grounding practices to stabilize your clients after releasing traumatic energy THERAPIST SKILLS 80 hours Trauma informed care Providing a safe, sensitive and supportive care for individuals who have experienced trauma Skills for workshop facilitation on channeling Kundalini energy Techniques to facilitate the process of Tantric De-armouring Massage Leading tantric breathwork sessions Creating and facilitating tantric workshops that will enhance intimacy between couples The art of holding space, providing a compassionate and non-judgmental presence Techniques to protect your own energy and the energy of others during healing sessions The training is facilitated by Alexis Alcalá InnerCamp founder Master Trainer Meet Alexis Alcalá, the founder of InnerCamp and the visionary behind Holosomatic Therapy®. With over 12 years of experience in Breathwork, Bodywork, and Energy Activation, Alexis blends scientific knowledge with spiritual wisdom, making ancient healing practices accessible and relevant for modern times. His journey into somatic therapies began after years in the corporate world, where disconnection and health challenges pushed him to seek deeper healing. Traditional therapy and coaching provided insights, but they couldn’t fully address the root causes of his struggles. It was through somatic work that Alexis not only reconnected with his body but also transformed his life and found profound healing beyond what conventional medicine had offered. During this process, he trained with some of the most respected mentors in the field, deepening his understanding of the body-mind connection and developing his own approach to holistic healing. In 2018, after facilitating healing experiences for thousands worldwide, Alexis founded InnerCamp with a bold mission: to spread Holosomatic Therapy® across the globe. Since then, InnerCamp has trained over 2,000 therapists and impacted the lives of hundreds of thousands. Today, his focus is on expanding this movement, ensuring that Holosomatic Therapy® reaches communities worldwide and becomes a powerful tool for transformation and healing. Marjolein Van Ommeren Master Trainer Marjolein strongly believes that we are all healers, and her holistic approach is based on this foundation. Her mission is to help people raise their vibration and restore balance in their lives by reconnecting them to their inner light. Marjolein promotes the wisdom of the Womb/Hara Awakening, an ancient, self-empowering practice that is all about returning to the Western world’s awareness, helping people reconnect to their true purpose and align their lives. Joanna Radkowska Master Trainer Counselor Joanna’s background is working with survivors of abuse and exploitation in a trauma-informed way to help them rebuild their lives, increase feelings of safety and security within themselves and in their surroundings, and offer a space where their voices are heard. Joanna’s constant pursuit of knowledge has taken her on a student journey, starting with her studies in Psychology to various holistic and talking therapies such as Reiki, Alchemical Healing, Clinical Hypnotherapy, Yoga and Meditation, Breathwork and Pranayama, Tantra and Womb Healing. Joanna believes that offering kindness, compassion and practising self-love are crucial when healing from any life difficulties, and it is her focus during sessions with clients. Jordan Head Master Trainer Jordan has 17 years of experience working within the health and wellness industry as a Personal Trainer, Nutrition Coach, Master Practitioner of Neuro Linguistic Programming and Breathwork coach. Jordan is passionate about supporting others in removing what holds them back, and directing their energy towards a more fulfilling experience of life through their authentic selves. Kevin Haesen Master Trainer Kevin Haesen is a seasoned guide in the realms of breathwork, energetic healing, yoga, and embodied awareness. With over 25 years of personal experience — and more than a decade of full-time professional work since 2013 — he has devoted his life to helping others reconnect with their inner vitality and truth. Based in Hasselt, Belgium, Kevin runs his own yogastudio Plooy together with his partner, where he holds space for deep inner journeys rooted in presence and compassion. His work blends ancient traditions with intuitive energetic guidance, offering participants a grounded yet transcendent experience. Alongside his group work and retreats, Kevin also coaches men in reclaiming integrated masculinity — helping them navigate purpose, emotional depth, and authentic presence in a world that often encourages disconnection. He has facilitated sessions and trainings across Europe, and his work has been featured on national television in Belgium. As a lifelong student of consciousness, he continues to explore the profound effects of meditation, breath, and movement on human potential. At Innercamp, Kevin brings his unique depth, playfulness, and grounded clarity to the Energetic Work Training — creating a space where transformation becomes tangible and energy becomes deeply personal. Testimonials See more testimonials JOIN THE INNERCAMP TRIBE What You Will Learn Guiding individuals and groups on a path of psychological, emotional, and spiritual transformation We know that at this point in your journey you are looking to become the best possible therapist you can be, to work with and touch the lives of hundreds of clients in a unique and profound way. Holosomatic Energy® is more than just Kundalini Activation—it&#8217;s a comprehensive approach that integrates Taoism, Tantric Breathwork, Somatic techniques, and Modern Psychology, all within a trauma-informed and scientifically-backed framework. This method not only clears blockages and releases trauma but also helps to reprogram the mind, aligning body, mind, and spirit for lasting resilience. At InnerCamp, we combine ancient spiritual practices with modern science to equip you with leading-edge skills to become the best facilitator you can be. Whether you&#8217;re new to healing or looking to deepen your expertise, we offer a clear, safe, and effective pathway to mastery. Become a HolosomaticEnergy® facilitator We know that you will want to use your new skills with your clients as soon as possible. So, we’ve developed an advanced program that gives you all the expertise you need to lead and facilitate five specialized workshops in just four months: Kundalini Activation Workshops. Guide individuals and groups, both in-person and online, through the powerful process of Kundalini activation. Tantric De-armouring Massages. Provide one-on-one, in-person sessions that release physical and emotional blockages. Tantric Breathwork Workshops. Lead transformative tantric breathwork sessions for groups or individuals, available both in-person and online. Facilitate intimate workshops for couples, enhancing their connection and energy exchange, offered both in-person and online. Transform lives with the InnerCamp Method As a facilitator we want to help you unlock your full potential and help your clients achieve balance in physical, emotional, and spiritual well-being. Perhaps you’ve already had some success as a facilitator but intuitively know you can help others to heal on an even deeper level. This program empowers you to lead transformative events &#8211; both online and in person &#8211; across one-on-one, couple, and group sessions. We know that at this point in your journey you are looking to become the best possible therapist you can be, to work with and touch the lives of hundreds of clients in a unique and profound way. Holosomatic Energy® is more than just Kundalini Activation—it&#8217;s a comprehensive approach that integrates Taoism, Tantric Breathwork, Somatic techniques, and Modern Psychology, all within a trauma-informed and scientifically-backed framework. This method not only clears blockages and releases trauma but also helps to reprogram the mind, aligning body, mind, and spirit for lasting resilience. At InnerCamp, we combine ancient spiritual practices with modern science to equip you with leading-edge skills to become the best facilitator you can be. Whether you&#8217;re new to healing or looking to deepen your expertise, we offer a clear, safe, and effective pathway to mastery. We know that you will want to use your new skills with your clients as soon as possible. So, we’ve developed an advanced program that gives you all the expertise you need to lead and facilitate five specialized workshops in just four months: Kundalini Activation Workshops. Guide individuals and groups, both in-person and online, through the powerful process of Kundalini activation. Tantric De-armouring Massages. Provide one-on-one, in-person sessions that release physical and emotional blockages. Tantric Breathwork Workshops. Lead transformative tantric breathwork sessions for groups or individuals, available both in-person and online. Facilitate intimate workshops for couples, enhancing their connection and energy exchange, offered both in-person and online. As a facilitator we want to help you unlock your full potential and help your clients achieve balance in physical, emotional, and spiritual well-being. Perhaps you’ve already had some success as a facilitator but intuitively know you can help others to heal on an even deeper level. This program empowers you to lead transformative events &#8211; both online and in person &#8211; across one-on-one, couple, and group sessions. The 6 Pillars of the Holosomatic Energy® Facilitator Training Module 1: Energy Healing Explore powerful energy modalities, including chakra balancing, Taoist energy work, aura healing, meridian activation, pineal gland activation, and womb &amp; hara healing to restore balance and vitality. Module 2: Trauma Release Utilize movement and somatic therapy exercises to release energetic blockages and prepare the body for deeper Kundalini Activation, all within a trauma-informed framework. Module 3: Tantric Breathwork Master breathwork techniques designed to awaken and amplify Kundalini energy, including So Hum Breathwork and other practices to energize and expand the body’s potential. Module 4: Womb/Hara Healing Deeply restorative energy and somatic practices designed to release emotional blockages, reconnect with the body's wisdom, and restore balance in the sacral area, supporting both physical and energetic well-being. Module 5: Tantric De-armouring Massage Learn hands-on Tantric de-armouring techniques to release stored tension and open the body’s energetic pathways for deeper transformation. Module 6: Kundalini Activation Dive into advanced Kundalini Activation practices, guiding clients through safe and profound energy awakenings for deep healing and expanded consciousness. Learn more about the Holosomatic Energy® Training Program: Check out the recording of our latest webinar to learn more about our method! You&#8217;ll also get the chance to experience an Energy Activation session yourself. Watch Webinar JOIN THE INNERCAMP TRIBE Who Is This Training For? Aspiring Facilitators Anyone who wants to become a certified TKundalini Activation facilitator and work with clients, regardless of prior experience. Kundalini Activation Facilitators Those who are already trained in Kundalini Activation and wish to expand their skills within a trauma-informed framework while integrating additional methods into their practice. Personal Growth Seekers Individuals looking for comprehensive more in-depth, professional training to build a strong foundation in Kundalini Activation, whether for self-practice or personal development— even if they are not sure if they want to facilitate the sessions right away. Supportive Friends &amp; Family Members Those who want to offer safe, trauma-informed Kundalini Activation &amp; De-armouring massage sessions to their loved ones while ensuring they have the proper knowledge and training, even if they don’t intend to build a business or work with clients professionally. Dates &amp; Prices Edition 12 online Jan 20, 2026 - Jun 02, 2026 Live sessions on Tuesdays Level 1: 20-Jan-26, 27-Jan-26, 3-Feb-26, 10-Feb-26, 17-Feb-26, 24-Feb-26, 3-Mar-26, 10-Mar-26, 17-Mar-26 Level 2: 7-Apr-26, 14-Apr-26, 21-Apr-26, 28-Apr-26, 5-May-26, 12-May-26, 19-May-26, 26-May-26, 2-Jun-26 100% Online Regular Price: 3499 EUR Early Bird Price: 2499 EUR 100% online format Small group (max 25 students) 18 2.5h Zoom live sessions Access to the training forever Periodical mentoring calls forever Globally recognized diploma Access to Business tools 18:30 - 21:00 *Amsterdam/Paris time zone See my local time Edition 13 hybrid Mar 24, 2026 - Jul 30, 2026 --> 5-day in-person Retreat in Centro Santillán, Málaga Centro Santillán, Málaga Carretera Macharaviaya k