the experience for the online trainings and 30 days prior to the start date of the experience for the hybrid trainings. INSTALLMENTS Secure your spot in the program while spreading out the cost over time. Upon selecting the payment in 3 equal installments option, the first installment will be charged immediately. The other 2 installments will be charged in the following 2 consecutive months. Book your spot 1070&euro; 3 installments 2999&euro; full price 1000&euro; deposit FULL PRICE Secure your spot in the training with a full upfront payment. DEPOSIT To secure your spot in the training, please pay the deposit now. The deposit serves as a confirmation of your participation, while the remaining balance can be settled at a later date. The final payment would be due 14 days prior to the start date of the experience for the online trainings and 30 days prior to the start date of the experience for the hybrid trainings. INSTALLMENTS Secure your spot in the program while spreading out the cost over time. Upon selecting the payment in 3 equal installments option, the first installment will be charged immediately. The other 2 installments will be charged in the following 2 consecutive months. Book your spot Choose format: Online Hybrid (In person + online) Year 2025: Choose dates: 20 Jan - 02 Jun Year 2025: Choose dates: 24 Mar - 30 Jul Total Cost: What's included in the training program Professional Training. Learn to facilitate Kundalini Activation workshops, Tantric De-armoring massages, Tantric Breathwork workshops, and Healing Circles. Earn a globally recognized diploma. Student facilitation sessions are included. Emotional support from a counselor is available to all students. Receive personalized feedback on assignments from an experienced trainer. Gain access to business tools. Flexible Learning Options. Choose between hybrid (in-person and online) or fully online training, both totaling 300 hours. Experience the best of both worlds with 5 days of in-person instruction complemented by 4 months of online coursework, or opt for our online program featuring weekly live sessions via Zoom. Globally Recognized Certification. Earn a diploma that is valid worldwide from an accredited training institution, ensuring you receive high-quality education and a respected certification upon completion. Rapid Career Development. Within just 4 months, you'll be equipped to organize workshops, sessions, and retreats. Tailored Therapeutic Skillset. Develop a unique therapeutic skill set that meets your individual needs. Our curated techniques eliminate the need for extensive searching, allowing you to focus on your growth and flexibility as a therapist. Holistic and Trauma-Informed Approach. Experience a comprehensive, trauma-informed, science-backed and embodied method that provides you with trusted and essential tools to support both yourself and your clients. Science-Backed Training Program. Our rigorous and effective curriculum blends the most pioneering and current science with holistic techniques to integrate and balance the mind, body, heart, and spirit. Extensive Hands-On Training. Engage in practical exercises designed to enhance your learning experience and deepen your skills. Read more Dual Focus on Professional Development and Personal Growth. This program not only trains future therapists and facilitators but also fosters self-healing and personal growth, helping you recognise and heal your own wounds, discovering your true self, power, and gifts. User-Friendly Learning Platform. Access our modern app and e-learning platform to study conveniently on your laptop or mobile device. Global Reach. Join over 2,000 participants from 45 countries who have successfully completed the Holosomatic Therapy® training since 2018. Structured Session Planning. Eliminate the stress of session structuring with our tested, step-by-step method that you can implement immediately. Lifetime Monthly Mentorship. Benefit from ongoing emotional support, private counseling, and personalized feedback on assignments, helping you navigate the challenges that arise as you step into your higher purpose. Vibrant Global Community. Connect with a supportive community where you can share your journey, celebrate successes, and overcome challenges together. Our community provides the encouragement and reflection necessary for personal growth, including “study buddies” to support you throughout the course. Affiliate Program Benefits. Earn commissions for referring friends to InnerCamp and enjoy discounts on future experiences. Business Support and Visibility. Receive guidance on connecting with clients and marketing your sessions, along with a listing in the InnerCamp Facilitators Directory as a certified therapist/facilitator. Student Facilitation Sessions. This training includes both online and in-person facilitation sessions, providing students with hands-on experience to practice and refine their facilitation skills throughout the program. Book your spot Frequently asked questions What is InnerCamp? Founded in 2018 by Alexis Alcalá, InnerCamp is a nurturing training institution dedicated to holistic therapy and personal development. We believe in creating a supportive sanctuary for those seeking to explore beyond conventional practices and our diverse range of programs and workshops is designed to empower you to become a highly effective holistic therapist. At InnerCamp, we blend alternative healing methods with solid scientific and psychological foundations, ensuring that you receive a well-rounded education that explores healing from multiple angles. Our compassionate team, composed of 20 experienced educators with over 10 years of teaching in various disciplines, is committed to guiding you on your journey. We also have a dedicated Research Department focused on scientific investigations, ensuring our content remains at the leading-edge of scientific discovery. With more than 2,000 students from 45 countries having studied the various Holosomatic Therapy® techniques with us, we have established ourselves as a leader in holistic training. Our registered brands, Holosomatic Therapy® and Holosomatic®, reflect our commitment to excellence in the field. Our programs offer a range of specializations, including breathwork therapy, somatic bodywork therapy, energy healing, cacao ceremony, available in both online and onsite formats. We are recognized for our transformative approach that seamlessly integrates ancient wisdom with modern techniques, helping you develop the skills needed to support others on their healing journeys. As an accredited school registered with the Complementary Medical Association and a member of the International Breathwork Foundation, InnerCamp is proud to provide CPD-certified training in Holosomatic Therapy®. Our dedication to holistic health has garnered us recognition as a leading provider in this field. At InnerCamp, our mission goes well beyond just training you. We aim to cultivate a vibrant community that inspires meaningful change in a world that so desperately needs it. Through our programs, not only will you gain valuable tools to help the lives of your clients, but you’ll develop methods for your own self-growth, trauma release, relationship harmonization — creating an inner and outer landscape that fosters self-love and consciousness expansion. Why should I join InnerCamp? - We have proven success, proudly training over 2,000 individuals on our courses over the last 5 years, empowering people just like you to make a positive impact through Energy Therapy. - Our Energy Therapy training program, available both online and in-person, offers an extensive 300-hour course designed to equip you with the knowledge and skills necessary for effective practice. You will delve into the healing power of Kundalini Activation, Energy Healing, Tantric Tantric Breathwork, De-armouring Massage, Tantric Intimacy, Trauma Release, and learn Therapist Success Strategies to empower you as you take your practice into the world. - We offer the expertise you need to thrive as a holistic therapist and make a lasting and meaningful impact in the lives of others. Whether you prefer the flexibility of online learning or the immersive experience of in-person training, our programs are designed to meet your needs wherever you are in the world. - InnerCamp courses benefit from globally recognised accreditation by three respected international organizations, ensuring that you receive a high-quality education that meets global standards. - Our dedicated and experienced trainers bring over 10 years of experience in working with clients and therapists from all over the world, offering you invaluable insights and support throughout your learning journey and beyond. - We focus on healing, not gurus. At InnerCamp, we prioritize the healing and transformation of individuals and communities over the idea of guru status. Your growth as a therapist is what truly matters to us and we do everything we can to help you become the most proficient and effective Holistic Therapist. - We provide a trauma-informed approach to ensure that you are able to support your clients safely and effectively, preventing any harm and fostering a deep sense of trust and genuine healing. Which Kundalini Activation technique/s exactly are you using in this program? It’s well known that many people experience challenges during Kundalini activation sessions, which can sometimes lead to trauma or illness. Our program, however, offers a holistic and therapeutic approach that prioritizes the safety and well-being of you and your future clients. Rather than simply activating Kundalini energy or pursuing unfocused catharsis, we focus on the mindful activation of energy that respects the body's readiness for Kundalini activation techniques. Our comprehensive and compassionate methodology addresses any potential blockages which can be worked through to prevent traumatic experiences. We use a range of techniques to create a balanced and supportive experience in preparation for Kundalini activation, including: - Energy Field Activation - Chakra Balancing - Breathwork - Meditation and Visualization - Neuroscience Principles - Somatic Techniques - Bandhas Work - Tantric Practices - Accessing Non-Ordinary States of Consciousness Our program is designed to safely and effectively prepare the body, alleviate blockages, and promote overall well-being while safely guiding participants through the profound journey of Kundalini awakening. What’s the difference between online and in-person training? In-Person: Our in-person courses include an intensive 5-day in-person training where you will engage in transformative practices to connect with your intuition and activate your energy. By the end of this immersive experience, you will be equipped to facilitate some of the most powerful energy healing techniques developed with scientific backing. Following this training, you will begin a 4-month online course (260 hours), which you can complete at your own pace within 6 months. While there are no live Zoom sessions, you will have access to monthly mentoring calls and all of InnerCamp’s virtual workshops. Upon successful completion, you will receive your InnerCamp Energy Activation Therapist Diploma. Online: In the online training program, you will participate in 18 live Zoom sessions (2.5 hours each) focused on intuitive connection and energy activation. This course also includes a 3-month online curriculum totaling 300 hours. Similar to the in-person program, it is designed to be completed within 4 months, with an extension of up to 6 months if you need more time. You will have access to monthly mentoring calls and all virtual workshops. After completing all course requirements, you will receive your InnerCamp Tantra Energy Activation Therapist Diploma. Which Holosomatic Therapy® Training should I take, Breath, Body, or Energy? If you are new to learning or offering healing practices, we recommend you begin your journey with Holosomatic Breath Therapy®. This is our foundational program and allows you to experience, embody, and master essential skills in inner connection, emotional regulation, and focused attention. For those who already possess a solid foundation and are seeking to deepen their understanding of bodily experiences and heal deeper layers of trauma, Holosomatic Body Therapy® is the ideal choice to take your kills to the next level. This program emphasizes bodywork techniques that facilitate the release of old traumas stored in the body, helping to alleviate tissue numbness and allowing your system to safely open up to more subtle vibrational frequencies—preparing you for higher levels of energetic activation and movement. Once you have established this essential groundwork, you may find that Holosomatic Energy Therapy® aligns best with your growth processes, both personally and in your Holistic Therapy practices with clients, enabling you to explore advanced energetic activation and movement. If I had the training a few years ago, would you recommend me to take it again? Is there a difference between the previous InnerCamp Tantra training and the Holosomatic ENERGY Therapy Training? The Holosomatic Energy Therapy® Training features a new and distinct curriculum that differs significantly from our previous courses, with only about 20% overlap. This innovative program focuses on the six foundational elements: Kundalini Activation, Energy Healing, Tantric De-armouring Massage, Tantric Breathwork, Tantric Intimacy, and Trauma Release Techniques. If you’re interested in enhancing your skills and deepening your journey with us, we’d be delighted to have you enroll in this transformative training. And, if you’ve been on the previous training we’ll be happy to offer a special discount for returning participants. It will be wonderful to see you again! What does this training include? - Expert guidance from senior teachers with online or in-person class options - Lifetime access to the online course, including all the videos and exclusive reading materials. - Structured learning with weekly tasks and personalized advice designed to enhance your skills. - Participate in all of InnerCamp’s virtual workshops for four months. - Benefit from exclusive discounts on additional InnerCamp experiences, courses, and events. - Access curated playlists to enhance your personal journey and your practice with clients. - Utilize our fully customizable templates for your sessions and events promotions. - Receive ongoing support with lifetime access to monthly mentoring calls and study partner meetings. - Connect with a vibrant, global community of Holistic Therapists just like you. - Earn an internationally recognized Diploma to facilitate sessions using the InnerCamp Method. - Get listed in the InnerCamp Facilitators Directory to enhance your professional visibility. - Free 1-on-1 session with the InnerCamp counsellor. Can I move at my own pace through the course? Yes, you can take your time with the course material. We understand that everyone learns at a different pace and sometimes moving slower can help you to retain the information better. However, it is important to be aware that this course requires you to attend live sessions in order to stay on track. This will ensure that you don’t fall behind and also allows you to interact with the instructors and other students in the course. Is there any deadline? After the program has officially ended, you have up to 3 months to complete the course on our platform in order to receive your certification. This is the final extension for the completion of the program. Does the training include examination? Yes, each level of our training comes with a final exam. The purpose of this examination is to ensure you are able to recognise, recall and show understanding what you have learned. The exam also covers your ability to select, organize and communicate relevant information in a variety of forms present and organize material clearly, use relevant terminology, and apply your knowledge and skill set to real-life situations. Are the assignments mandatory? Yes, assignments are a key part of the learning experience. They’re crafted to help you deepen your understanding of the theories, concepts, and methods we cover during your course of study. While they are mandatory, they are also an opportunity for personal growth and self-discovery, allowing you to gain valuable insights into yourself and how you relate to the material. We believe these assignments will enrich your journey and support you in becoming more connected with your own learning process. If I booked the online training, should I turn my camera on during live sessions? Yes, we ask that you keep your camera on during live sessions to ensure active participation and engagement. This helps create a connected and focused learning environment between you, your instructors, and other students on the course. If you have any challenges with attendance due to work or other commitments, please let us know in advance, and we’ll do our best to accommodate you. Your presence and visibility are important to us and enhance the overall learning experience. How does the pricing work? We have three payment options available: 1. Full payment upfront: Paying the entire amount for the training program in a single payment at the time of registration. 2. Deposit payment: This option requires customers to pay a deposit of 500 euros to secure their spot in the training program. The remainder of the balance is then due 2 weeks (for online programs) or 1 month (for onsite/hybrid programs) prior to the start date of the program. 3. Installment payments: This option allows customers to spread the cost of the training program over several months. The payment plan involves paying the total cost of the program in equal installments, with each payment charged monthly from the customer's card. My training program has not started yet but can I cancel and get a refund? Yes, you can cancel your program before it starts. Refunds depend on the cancellation date and program type, as outlined in our Cancellation Policy. We offer flexible terms, including full or partial refunds or credit for future bookings. For details, please review our Terms of Service at https://innercamp.com/terms/, Chapter 8. My training program has started but can I cancel and get a refund? Whilst we do understand that circumstances can change, and we’re here to help you when something arises, refunds are not available once the training program has started. However, you can transfer your enrollment to a future program for a fee of 300 EUR plus any price difference. Alternatively, in certain situations, we may be able to offer you credit toward a future program with InnerCamp. Please refer to our Cancellation and Refund Policy for more details at this link https://innercamp.com/terms/, Chapter 8. My training program has finished but I didn't participate; can I get a refund? We understand that sometimes things don’t always go as planned. If the program you booked onto has finished and you were unable to participate, a refund isn’t available. However, you can transfer your spot to a future session within three months for a 600 EUR admin fee plus any price difference. If you need to transfer after this period, you’ll need to pay the full current price for the new session. For more details, please check our Terms of Service at https://innercamp.com/terms/, Chapter 8. How much effort is required per week? For our online courses, we recommend approximately 10 hours per week of dedicated time, which includes the Zoom sessions. For the in-person courses, in addition to the face-to-face contact hours, we recommend an extra 6 hours per week. To make the most of your time at Innercamp, we also suggest you participate in our other community activities. If I booked the online training, should I attend all live sessions? It’s best to attend all live sessions, yes. At Inercamp we require a minimum attendance of 75% for the required live sessions of the course for Level 1 and 100% for Level 2. It would be best to make sure you are able to join in with all the scheduled dates when you book onto the course. What are the certification requirements? To be eligible for the Therapist Diploma, please ensure you meet the following requirements: ONLINE TRAINING - Maintain a minimum attendance rate of 75% for the live sessions. - Successfully complete the course on our e-learning platform and obtain approval for all assignments from the InnerCamp team - Keep the camera on in the live sessions and actively participate in the class and the practices. - Facilitate live in all students facilitating sessions according to the requirements of your course. IN-PERSON TRAINING - Join the in-person training and actively participate in all course activities - Successfully complete the online course on our e-learning platform and obtain approval for all assignments from the InnerCamp team. We encourage you to stay committed and engaged as you progress through your chosen program. Completing the course and earning your certification is a testament to your dedication and achievement. What if I cannot keep up with my current course, can I move my spot to the next edition and start over? We understand that sometimes life can get in the way of our educational pursuits and that it can be difficult to keep up with course requirements in some circumstances. If the program has started already and you’d like to move your spot to the next edition, you can do so for an additional fee of 300 EUR plus the price difference if any, in accordance with our Terms of Service. Section 8, Cancellation and Refund Policy. Who is a study buddy? Upon enrollment, all students are matched with a study buddy to support them on their journey. A study buddy is a",60037
